\v 6 \x - \xo 19:6 \xt God…®n Araziba 1:17; Onger Akaba 82:1\x*Egha kotiaba tuis…®zir jasba, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa gumazamizibar ingangarim gamir puvat…®. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarim gami, a uab…® ia ko iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia kotiaba tuis…®ghamin dughiabar, ia uari uan araziba bagh derav…®ra gan.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 19:7 \xt God…®n Araziba 10:17; Aposel 10:34; Rom 9:14; 1 Pita 1:17\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God, kotiam…®n aven, guiz…®n arazim giragh kotiaba baraghamin araziba, ko uan namakabar akabar akurvaghamin araziba ko, gumazamiziba ia apezeper dag…®aba ia dan…®ngamin araziba, arazir kaba God bar dar aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia gumazir kotiaba tuis…®ziba, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiating…®va bar an apengan ik…®, egh deraghv…®ra uan arazibar gan.‚Äù 
