\v 11 Ia derav…®ram oragh. Gumazir pumuning ian faragh mang…® kotiabar ingangaribar ganam. Gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Araziba ab…®gha da munasir kotiaba baraghamin dughiam…®n, God…®n ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Amaria, ian kotiabar faragh mangam. Eght…® gumazamiziba gavman…®n araziba ab…®gha da munasir kotiaba baraghamin dughiam…®n, Ismael…®n otarim Sebadaia, a Judan gumazir dapanim, a ian kotiabar faragh mangam. Eght…® kotiabar ingangaribar, Livaiba ian akurvagham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumazir arazir aghuibagh amiba ko iti, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia atiatingan kogh tuivigh gavgavigh ingangarir kaba bar dar amu.‚Äù 
