\v 5 Egha me iza Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba ko me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n danganir igiar me uari akuvamin uari akufa. Ez…® Atrivim Jehosafat ghua men tong…®n tugha, kamagh…®n God ko m…®gei,  
\v 6 ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® en inazir afeziabar God, n…® uan Nguibam…®n ikiava, nguazim…®n ik…®ziba bar me gativagha men gari. N…® gavgavir bar ekiam iti. Eght…® gumazitam n…® m…®sogh n…® ab…®raghan kogham.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 20:7 \xt Aisaia 41:8; Jems 2:23\x*O en God, n…® fo, e Israelia n…®n roroam Abraham…®n ovavir boriba, e n…®n gumazamizibara. N…® gumazamizir fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n apiaziba, n…® me batoghez…® me are, eght…® nguazir kam, a en nguazimra ik…® mamagh…®ra ikiasa n…® e gan…®ngi.  
\v 8 Ez…® e dughiar ruarim…®n nguazir kam…®n ikegha g…®fa. En inazir afeziaba fom…®ra n…®n borogh…®n mang…®, n…®n ziam fasa D…®penir kam…®n ingari. Egha me an ingarigha g…®vazir dughiam…®n, me kamagh…®n n…® ko m…®g…®a ghaze,  
\v 9 ‚ÄòIkiav…®ra Itir God, os…®mt…®zitam e batogham, o apaniba iz…® e ko m…®sogham, o ar…®mariar kurar ekiatam otogham, o dagheba otevir dughiar ruaritam e batoght…®, e iz…® D…®penir kam…®n guam…®n n…®n damazim…®n tugham. D…®penir kam, a danganir e n…®n borogh…®n iz…® n…®n ziam famim. Egh e os…®mt…®zir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gh uarir akurvaghs…® n…®n azangs…®gham. Eght…® n…® en d…®mdiam baragh uam e iniam.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 20:10 \xt God…®n Araziba 2:4-19\x*Egha Atrivim Jehosafat ua kamagh…®n God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® Amonia ko Moapia ko Idomian ganigha g…®fa, me e m…®soghasa ize. Bar fom…®ra, en inazir afeziaba Isip ategha iza ik…®zir kabar nguazim…®n otivir dughiam…®n, n…® en inazir afeziaba ataghiz…®, me me ko m…®soghezir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, en inazir afeziaba me gitagha, me gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®.  
\v 11 Ez…® me dat…®r…®gh…®n tong arazir aghuir en inazir afeziaba me gamizibagh n…®ghn…®zir pu. Puvat…®. Me bar arazir kuram gamua e ko m…®soghasa. Me nguazir n…® uab…® e gan…®ngizir kam…®n e batueghasa izegha g…®fa.  
\v 12 \x - \xo 20:12 \xt Onger Akaba 25:15; 121:1-2\x*O, en God, m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rir kaba e m…®soghasava ami. Ez…® e me ko m…®soghamin gavgaviba puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® uab…® bar puv me damigh. Bar guizbang…®ra, e fozir puvat…®, e manmagh…®n damuam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e uarir akurvaghasa n…® baghav…®ra gara iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 13 Dughiar kam…®n, Judan gumaziba uan amuiroghboriba sara, me bar mogh…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n an D…®penim…®n borogh…®n tuivighav iti.  
\v 14 Ez…® Livaibar mav, an ziam Jahasiel, a gumazamizir kabar tong…®n tughav iti. Jahasiel, a Sekaraian otarim, ez…® Sekaraia, a Benaian otarim, ez…® Benaia, a Jeiel…®n otarim, ez…® Jeiel, a Matanian otarim. Gumazir kaba bar mogh…®ra, me Livain gumazim Asap…®n ovavir boriba. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Duam pamten iza Jahasiel giz…®vaz…®ma,  
\v 15 \x - \xo 20:15 \xt Ua Me Ini 14:13; God…®n Araziba 1:29-30; 2 Eghaghaniba 32:7\x*\x - \xo 20:15-17 \xt God…®n Araziba 20:1-4\x*a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Atrivim Jehosafat, ko ia Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamiziba ko ia Judaba bar, ia derav…®ram oragh. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a kamagh…®n ia m…®gei: Ia m…®dorozir gumazir av…®rir kam…®n atiating naviba os…®man mark…®. M…®dorozir kam, kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizimra. A ian bizim puvat…®.  
\v 16 Apaniba gurum m…®zaraghan ia m…®soghs…® Sis…®n m…®ghs…®am…®n ghuanadir tuavim…®n izam. Eght…® ia mang…® Jeruel…®n gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n borogh…®n, aruem anadi nagh…®n danganir zarim…®n me batogham.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 20:17 \xt Ua Me Ini 14:13-14; D…®boboniba 14:9; 2 Eghaghaniba 15:2\x*Ia uari m…®dorozir kam…®n m…®soghan kogham. Puvat…®. Ia mang…® m…®soghamin danganim…®n pura tuivigh ik…® gan, eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian akuragh m…®dorozir kam damuam. Ia Jerusalem ko Judan danganibar itir gumazamiziba, ia atiating naviba os…®man mark…®. Ia gurum m…®zaraghan m…®dorozim bagh mang…®, eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God ia ko ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® me akar kam baraghizir dughiam…®n, Atrivim Jehosafat tevimning ap…®righa uan guam nguazim m…®tua. Ez…® Judaba ko Jerusalemia bar, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n nguazim giregha an ziam fe.  
\v 19 Ez…® Livain anabam…®n Kohat ko Koran adarazi d…®kavigha pamtem…®n dia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God, an ziam fe. 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® bar m…®zaraghara, me d…®kavigha Tekoan nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®n itir gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n mangasava amua iti. Me t…®ghar Jerusalem atagh…®raghamin dughiam…®n, Atrivim Jehosafat kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Judaba ko Jerusalemia, ia oragh! Ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n ik…®, egh tuivigh gavgafigh. Egh ia God…®n akam inigha izir gumazibar akaba n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim dar ik…®, egh ia uan apaniba ab…®ragham.‚Äù  
\v 21 Egha atrivim uaghan gumazamizibar n…®ghn…®zibagh foghasa men azangs…®si, egha g…®n, a m…®dorozir gumazibar faragh mang…®, ighiar kam bangasa me am…®sefe: Ez…® me kamagh…®n ighiam bati. 
\b  
\q1 ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God…®n Araziba bar zue, 
\q2 ez…® arazir kam, mati an kurkazir aghuim. 
\q1 E bizir kabagh n…®ghn…®gh, 
\q2 egh an ziam f…® ighiaba bangam. 
\q1 Ikiav…®ra Itir God zurara en apangkuvigha mamagh…®ra iti. 
\q2 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, e a m…®namam.‚Äù 
\b  
\p  
\v 22-23 Jehosafat uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko zuir dughiam…®n, gumazir ighiam batiba, me d…®kavigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam famin ighiabagh ami. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Amonia ko Moapia ko Idomian m…®dorozir gumazibagh amiz…®ma, me uarira uarir atara uariv sosi. Amonia ko Moapia, faragha Idomia ko m…®sogha, bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha g…®n Amonia ko Moapia uari uariv sogha bar uarigh as…®ghas…®ki.  
\v 24 Ez…® Judan m…®dorozir gumaziba ghua gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n itir tauan mam…®n oto, kar tauan m…®dorozir gumaziba ikia apaniba bagha garim. Egha me apaniba bagha garava avenge. Me apanibar kuabar garima, da pura tintinibar nguazim…®n irav iti, ez…® me d…®gavir kuram gami. Men tav angam…®ra itir puvat…®, me bar mogh…®ra ariaghire. 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® Atrivim Jehosafat uan adarazi ko, gumazir kuar kabar tong…®n ghua garima, bizir bar av…®riba iti. Ez…® me dagheba ko korotiaba ko bizir bar aghuir av…®rir maba ini. Biziba bar av…®raseme, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me aruer pumuning ko m…®kezim…®n bizir kaba isav…®ra iti.  
\v 26 Egha namba 4…®n aruem…®n, me iza danganir zarir mam…®n uari akuvagha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God men akuragha amizir bizim g…®n…®ghn…®gha, an ziam fe. Bizir kam bang…®n, dughiar kam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, me danganir kam kamagh…®n a d…®bori, God…®n Ziam Fer Danganir Zarim.  
\v 27 Ikiav…®ra Itir God men akuragha men apaniba ab…®ra, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Jehosafat faragha zuima Judaba ko Jerusalemian gumaziba an g…®n ikia, me bar akuegha uamategha Jerusalem…®n zui.  
\v 28 Egha me gitabav sogha s…®ghabagh iviava Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n aven zui, egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n ghua ziar ekiam a gan…®di.  
\v 29 Ez…® kantrin igharazibar atriviba ko gumazir dapaniba kamagh…®n oraki, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Israelian akuragha men apanibav soghez…®, me bar ariaghire.  
\v 30 Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar deraghav…®ra Jehosafat…®n kantrin gari, kamagh…®n amiz…®, m…®dorozitam uam otozir puvat…®z…®, Jehosafat uan gumazamiziba ko avughsi. 
\s1 Atrivim Jehosafat areme 
\r (1 Atriviba 22:41-50) 
\p  
\v 31 Jehosafat azenir 35plan ikia atrivim…®n oto, egha 25plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. An amebam, Silhin guivim, an ziam Asuba.  
\v 32 Jehosafat uan afeziam Asa faragha ikiava amiz…® mogh…®n, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh ami.  
\v 33 \x - \xo 20:33 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 17:6; 19:3\x*Egha bizir vam…®ra, an a gamizir puvat…®, a m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fer danganibagh as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Ez…® gumazamiziba uaghan deragha uan inazir afeziabar God…®n g…®nt…®gha tugha gavgavizir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 34 Atrivim Jehosafat amizir arazir igharaziba bar, a faragha atrivim…®n otozir dughiam…®n ikegha ghua an aremezir dughiam…®n eghaghaniba, ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Hananin Otarim Jehun Eghaghaniba. Ez…® ak…®nafarir kam, ak…®nafarir bar ekiam…®n aven iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghanibar Ak…®nafarim. 
\p  
\v 35 Dughiar mam, Atrivim Jehosafat Israelian Atrivim Ahasia ko poro, ez…® atrivir kam arazir bar kurar av…®ribagh ami.  
\v 36 Egha aning uaning inigh biziba ater kantri Tarsis…®n mangasa kurir ekiabar ingari. Ez…® aning…®n ingangarir gumaziba Esiongeber…®n kurir ekiar kabar ingari.  
\v 37 Ez…® Dodavahun otarim Elieser, a Maresan nguibar ekiam…®n gumazim, a God…®n akar bar gavgavim…®n kamagh…®n Jehosafat m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® atrivir kuram Ahasia ko roroam gami. Kamagh amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God gua ingarizir kurir ekiabagh as…®ghasigham.‚Äù Ez…® kurir kaba ghua bar ikuvigha Tarsis…®n mangan ibura. 
\c 21  
\p  
\v 1 Egha g…®n Atrivim Jehosafat uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®ma, me Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n, an inazir afeziabar kuaba afezir danganim…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim Jehoram an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\ms1 Atrivim Jehoram…®n eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 21) 
\s1 Jehoram Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 8:17-24) 
\p  
\v 2 \x - \xo 21:2 \xt 2 Atriviba 8:16-24\x*Atrivim Jehoram dozir 6pla iti. Men ziabar kara: Asaria, Jehiel, Sekaraia, Asarian igharazim, Maikel ko Sefatia. Jehoram ko 6plan gumazir kaba, me bar Judan Atrivim Jehosafat…®n otariba.  
\v 3 Jehosafat gol ko silvan av…®rim ko bizir ivezir bar p…®n koziba isa uan borir kabagh an…®ngi. Egha a uaghan Judan nguibar ekiar d…®vazir bar gavgavim av…®nizibar ganamin ingangariba me gan…®ngi. Jehoram, a Jehosafat…®n otarir ivariam, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Jehosafat uan danganim inigh atrivim…®n ikiasa anem…®sefe.  
\v 4 Jehoram atrivim…®n otozir dughiam…®n, a uan kantri bagha gavgavigha, bar uan doziba ko Judan gumazir dapanir mabav soghez…® me ariaghire. 
\p  
\v 5 Jehoram 32plan azeniba ikiava atrivim…®n oto, egha a 8plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti.  
\v 6 A Israelian Atrivim Ahap…®n, guivim…®n iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an Ahap…®n adarazi ko Israelian atrivir igharazibar arazir kurabar g…®nt…®si. Egha arazir kurar av…®riba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami.  
\v 7 \x - \xo 21:7 \xt 1 Atriviba 11:36\x*Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Judan kantri gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan ingangarir gumazim, Atrivim Devit g…®n…®ghn…®si. A fom…®ra Devit ko akar d…®k…®r…®zim gamua ghaze, Devit…®n ik…®zibar tong…®n gumazitam zurara atrivim…®n ikiam, eght…® Devit…®n lam…®n angazangarim mungeghan kogham. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God akar d…®k…®r…®zir kam g…®n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a Judan kantri gas…®ghas…®ghan aghua. 
\p  
\v 8 \x - \xo 21:8 \xt Jenesis 27:40\x*Jehoram Judan atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Idomian gumazamiziba an akam batogha an apengan ikian aghua. Egha me uarir ganasa atrivir mam am…®sefe.  
\v 9 Ez…® Jehoram uan m…®dorozir gumazir dapaniba ko karis bar tuiva m…®sozir gumaziba inigha, Idomia m…®soghasa zui. Me ghua otiviz…®, Idomian gumaziba iza Jehoram…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ek…®arugha me m…®soghasa. Ez…® d…®magarim…®n Jehoram m…®dorozir gumazir karisbar zuiba inigha, bar pamtem m…®sogha me adugha ghue.  
\v 10 Egha, Judaba Idomia d…®kab…®razir puvat…®. Ez…® Idomian gumazamiziba, uari uan kantri gativagha ikia iza dat…®r…®gh…®n tu. Jehoram Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan inazir afeziabar God ak…®rim ragha a gasara. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, dughiar kam…®n, Lipnan nguibam…®n gumazamiziba uaghan akaba batogha, ua Judabar apengan itir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® Jehoram uaghan Judan kantrin m…®ghs…®abar itir danganibar asebar ziaba fasa danganibar ingari. Egha a Juda ko Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n gumazamizibagh ekuiz…®, me ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasaragha, an damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami. 
\p  
\v 12 Dughiar mam, God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Elaija, Atrivim Jehoram bagha ak…®nafarir mam osirigha anemaga ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a n…®n ovavim Devit…®n God, akam kamagh…®n n…®n iti: N…® uan afeziam Atrivim Jehosafat ko n…®n inazim Atrivim Asa, n…® aning…®n arazir aghuibar g…®nt…®zir puvat…®.  
\v 13 N…® Israelian atrivir arazir kurabagh amibar g…®n ghua, Judaba ko Jerusalemia getuima, me ak…®rim ragha God gasara. N…® Atrivim Ahap uan adarazi ko Israelia gamiz…® mogh…®ra n…® a gami. Egha n…® uan dozibav soghez…®, me ariaghire. Me gumazir aghuiba, egha men araziba bar n…®n arazibagh afira.  
\v 14 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God n…®n gumazamiziba ko, n…®n amuiba ko boriba sara paz…®v…®ra ia damuva, n…®n biziba bar dagh as…®ghasigham.  
\v 15 Eght…® n…® uab…®, ar…®mariar bar kuram n…®n muriar averiam…®n ikiam. Eght…® dughiabar vaghvagh, ar…®mariar kam bar ekeveght…®, n…®n evenavim asigh…®r…®gham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Filistiaba ko Arebian Itiopian nguazim…®n borogh…®n itibagh amiz…®, me Jehoram…®n an…®ngaghe.  
\v 17 Egha me iza kantri Juda m…®sogha, Atrivim Jehoram…®n d…®penim…®n itir biziba bar ada inigha ghu. Egha me an amuiba ko an otariba inigha ghue. Egha an otarir abuananam inigha ghuzir puvat…®, an ziam Joahas, an ziar igharazim Ahasia. 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® bizir kabar g…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ar…®mariar bar kuram gamiz…®, an atrivim…®n muriam…®n oto. Ar…®mariar kam a g…®vaghan kogham.  
\v 19 Ar…®mariar kam an itima, azenir pumuning g…®fa, ez…® Jehoram…®n evenavim asiaghir…®z…®, a m…®zazir bar kuram inigha areme. Ez…® Judan gumazamiziba a g…®n…®ghn…®ghasa avir ekiatam ar…®zir puvat…®, mati me an ovavibagh amiz…® mok…®n. 
\p  
\v 20 \x - \xo 21:20 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 24:25; 28:27; Jeremaia 22:18; 22:28\x*Jehoram azenir 32pla ikia atrivim…®n oto, egha 8plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. Ez…® an aremezir dughiam…®n, gumazitam an apangkuvizir puvat…®. Me atriviba afir danganim…®n anefazir puvat…®, me Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n anefa. 
\c 22  
\ms1 Atrivim Ahasia ko Atrivir Amizim Atalian eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 22) 
\s1 Ahasia Judan atrivim…®n oto 
\r (2 Atriviba 8:25-29; 9:21-28) 
\p  
\v 1 Jehoram atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Arebian gumazir maba m…®dorozir gumazir maba inigha Judan iza, an otarir ekiaba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha me Jehoram…®n otarir abuananam Ahasia m…®soghezir puvat…®.  
\v 2 Ez…® Ahasia 42plan azeniba ikia, egha atrivim…®n oto. Egha azenir vam…®ran Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike. An amebam Atalia, a Israelian Atrivim Omrin igiam.  
\v 3 An amebam n…®ghn…®zir kurabar an sure gami, kamagh…®n amiz…®, an Ahap…®n ik…®zim…®n arazir kurabagh ami.  
\v 4 An afeziam aremezir dughiam…®n g…®n, an Ahap…®n adarazi iniz…®, me n…®ghn…®ziba a gan…®dima, a men n…®ghn…®zibar g…®n ghuz…®, bizir kam bang…®n an araziba bar ikuvigha a gas…®ghas…®si. Ez…® Atrivim Ahasia arazir kuraba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami, mati Ahap…®n ik…®zim amiz…® mok…®n.  
\v 5 Egha Atrivim Ahasia gumazir kabar akam baregha ghua Israelian Atrivim Joram…®n porogha a ko ghua, aning Sirian Atrivim Hasael m…®sosi. Me Ramot…®n nguibar ekiam…®n borogh…®ra uariv sosi, a Gileat…®n Distrigh…®n itir nguibam. Ez…® Sirian m…®dorozir gumaziba Joram b…®raz…®, a bar ikufi.  
\v 6 Ez…® Joram m…®dorozim ategha ghua, Jesril…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ikia, ua deraghasa m…®zua iti. A Jesril…®n ikiav…®ra itima, Atrivim Ahasia an ganasa ghu. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® God fogha g…®fa, Atrivim Ahasia mang…® Joram…®n gan ikiamin dughiar kam…®n, an a gas…®ghasigham. Egha dughiar kam…®n Ahasia ghua Joram ko ikia aning ghua Nimsin otarim Jehu bato. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Ahap…®n ik…®zim gas…®ghas…®ghasa, Jehu am…®sefe.  
\v 8 Ez…® Jehu, Ahap…®n ik…®zim gas…®ghas…®gha ghua Judabar gumazir dapanir maba ko Ahasian dozibar otariba bato. Gumazir kaba Ahasian ingangaribagh ami. Ez…® Jehu bar me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire.  
\v 9 A me m…®soghez…® me ariaghiregha g…®vaz…®, an Atrivim Ahasia buri. Ez…® Ahasia Samarian nguibam…®n modogha iti. Ez…® gumazir maba an ganigha a inigha Jehu bagha izez…®, an a m…®soghez…® an areme. Ez…® me Ahasian kuam purama anetaghiz…® a itir puvat…®. Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, Ahasia, an Atrivim Jehosafat…®n igiam, Jehosafat bar uan navir averiam…®n aven Ikiav…®ra Itir God baghav…®ra iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me Ahasian kuam isa mozim…®n anefa. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Ahasian ik…®zim…®n aven, Judabar atrivim…®n ik…®va men ganamin gumazitam ua itir puvat…®. 
\s1 Atalia Judabar atrivir amizim…®n oto 
\r (2 Atriviba 11:1-3) 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Atrivim Ahasian amebam Atalia kamagh…®n akam baraki, an otarim Ahasia aremegha g…®fa. Ez…® a zuam…®ra m…®dorozir gumazibav kemez…®, me Judan atrivibar ik…®zim…®n gumaziba bar me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.  
\v 11 Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba Ahasian otarim Joas m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…®. Me kamagh…®n fozir puvat…®, Atrivim Jehoram…®n guivim Jehoseba, an Atrivim Ahasian buaramizim, an ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiadan amuim, amizir kamra, a moga atrivim…®n otarir aremeghamibar tong…®n Joas inigha, amizir an ganamim ko, aning isa danganir me daguivsiaba ar…®zim…®n aven aning modo. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Atalia Joas m…®soghez…® an aremezir puvat…®.  
\v 12 Ez…® Jehoseba 6plan azenibar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven Joas modoz…® an a ko iti. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, Atalia Judan atrivir amizim…®n ikiav…®ra iti. 
\c 23  
\ms1 Atrivim Joas…®n eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 23--24) 
\s1 Me Joas am…®sevez…®, an atrivim…®n oto 
\r (2 Atriviba 11:4-16) 
\p  
\v 1 Atalia atrivir amizim…®n itima, an namba 7…®n azenim…®n, God…®n ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada bizitam damuasa n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim iti. Egha a 100plan m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir dapaniba ko m…®geima, me an akuraghasa a ko akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim gami. Gumazir dapanir kabar ziabar kara: Jeroham…®n otarim Asaria, ko Jehohanan…®n otarim Ismael, ko Obet…®n otarim Asaria, ko Adaian otarim Masea, ko Sikrin otarim Elisafat.  
\v 2 Gumazir dapanir kaba Judan nguibar ekiaba bar dar ghua, Livaiba ko Israelian ik…®zibar gumazir dapaniba inigha Jerusalem…®n ize. 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 23:3 \xt 2 Samuel 7:12\x*Ez…® gumazir kaba bar mogh…®ra God…®n D…®penim…®n uari akuvagha, Atrivim Joas…®n apengan ikiasa akar d…®k…®r…®zir gavgavim gami. Ez…® Jehoiada kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God akar d…®k…®r…®zim kamagh…®n a gamigha ghaze, dughiabar zurara atriviba Devit…®n ik…®zim…®n otivam. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ia iz…® Joas…®n ganigh. An Atrivim Ahasian otarim, an atrivim…®n otivam.  
\v 4 Ez…® e dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n damuam. Ia God…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ko Livaiba, Sabat…®n aruem…®n ingangarim damus…® iz…®, 3plan okoruabar uari tuiragh. Okoruatam, God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akabar ganam.  
\v 5 Eght…® okoruar namba 2, atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n gan, eght…® okoruar namba 3, tiar akar me kamagh…®n d…®borim, Jesot, me an gan. Eght…® gumazamiziba bar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n uari akuvir danganir ekiam…®n ik…®.  
\v 6 Ofa gamir gumaziba ko Livain men akurvaziba, merara God…®n damazim…®n zue, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mangam. Ia gumazamizir igharaziba ateght…®, me aven mangan mark…®. Gumazamizir igharaziba, God m…®kemez…® mogh…®n azenan ik…®.  
\v 7 Livaiba uan m…®dorozir sababar suigh atrivim Joas ek…®arugh, bar deraghv…®ram an gan. Eght…® a danganir manam…®n mang…®t…®, me a sara mang…®. Eght…® gumazitam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven iz…®t…®, Livaiba a m…®sueght…® an aremegh.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 8 Ez…® Livaiba ko Judan gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra, ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiadan akar kam…®n g…®n zui. Egha Sabat…®n dughiam…®n, gumazir dapaniba, gumazir ingangarim ag…®vagha avughsasa amir kaba, ko gumazir men danganiba iniamiba, gumazir dapanir kaba bar men akua Jehoiada bagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n izi.  
\v 9 Dughiar kam…®n, Atrivim Devit…®n afuziba ko orar ekiaba ko doziba, da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n iti. Ez…® Jehoiada bizir kaba inigha m…®dorozir gumazibar dapanibagh an…®ngi.  
\v 10 Egha Jehoiada, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n d…®vazim…®n danganiba bar dar m…®tivasa gumaziba amangi. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n uari bagha danganiba inigha, saut…®n amadaghan ikegha ghua not…®n amadaghan tu. Me uaghan ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n tuivighav ikia, m…®dorozir sababa suigha, atrivim ek…®arugha bar deraghv…®ra gara iti.  
\v 11 M…®dorozir gumaziba uari ak…®righa m…®zua itima, ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada uan otariba ko, Joas…®n akua azenan iza, atrivibar dapanir asuam Joas…®n dapanim garu. Egha Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim itir ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir mam a gan…®ngi. Egha me g…®n oliv…®n borem Joas…®n dapanim gingegha anem…®sevez…®, an atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® gumazamiziba bar akuegha kamagh…®n dei, ‚ÄúJoas dughiar ruarim…®n atrivim…®n ikiam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Atrivir Amizim Atalia orazima n…®g…®nir dafam oto. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumaziba ko gumazamiziba bar akuegha d…®a ivemara arua atrivim…®n ziam fe. Ez…® atrivir amizim uan d…®penim ategha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n danganir gumazamiziba uari akuva itim…®n zui.  
\v 13 A ghua otogha garima, atrivir igiam, atriviba ami mogh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n guam…®n itir guarir ak…®nim…®n borogh…®n tughav iti. Egha a m…®dorozir gumazibar dapaniba ko gumazir s…®ghabagh ivibar garima, me atrivir igiam…®n borogh…®n iti. A uaghan garima gumazamiziba bar akuegha, men marazi uaghan is…®ghabagh ivi. Ez…® ighiabagh amir gumaziba uan gitaba ko buabav soghava ighiabagh amua men faragha zui. Ez…® Atalia puv atara uan korotiam ab…®gha d…®a ghaze, ‚ÄúIa gumazamizir kuraba. Ia bar arazir kuram gamua na ab…®nasa.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 14 Ez…® Jehoiada Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n borogh…®n Atalia m…®sueght…® an aremeghan an aghua. Egha a kamagh…®n m…®dorozir gumazir dapanibav gei, ‚ÄúIa Atalian suiraght…®, m…®dorozir gumaziba anek…®arugh a kurugh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n azenan mang…®. Eght…® gumazitam an g…®n mang…®t…®, ia gumazir kam m…®sueght…® an aremegh.‚Äù  
\v 15 Ez…® me Atalian suiragha, a inigha God…®n D…®penim ategha ghua atrivim…®n d…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazir hoziaba aven zuir tiar akam…®n aven ghugha, a m…®soghez…® an areme. 
\s1 Ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada,  // Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n g…®n mangasa  // gumazamizibar akurvasi 
\r (2 Atriviba 11:17-21) 
\p  
\v 16 God…®n ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada, Atrivim Joas ko gumazamizibar akurvazi, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gamua ghaze, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n gumazamizibara ikiam. Egha a uaghan atrivim ko gumazamizibar akuraz…®, me uarir tong…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gami.  
\v 17 Egha g…®n gumazamiziba asem Bal…®n ziam fer d…®penim…®n ghua, bar a gas…®ghas…®ki. Egha me ofa gamir dakoziba ko asem Bal…®n marvir guabagh as…®ghas…®ki. Egha me ofa gamir dakozir kabar borogh…®n Bal…®n ofa gamir gumazim Matan m…®soghez…® an areme.  
\v 18 Ez…® Jehoiada Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven itir ingangaribar ganasa, Livain adarazir tong…®n, God…®n ofa gamir gumazir maba ko Livain igharaziba sara me am…®sefe. Ik…®zir kamning, Atrivim Devit fom…®ra ingarasa men ovavibav kemez…® mogh…®ra me ingari. Egh me Moses Osirizir Araziba m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar amu. Egh me Devit m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ofa damuamin dughiam…®n, me buabav sogh ighiabagh amir gumazibav k…®mt…®, me ighiar bar akongezibar amu.  
\v 19 Egha Jehoiada Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n tiar akabar ganasa Livain maba am…®sefe. Eght…® Livain kaba bar deraghv…®ra tiar akabar gant…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®zir gumazamiziba aven mangan kogham. 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® Jehoiada, m…®dorozir gumazibar dapaniba ko, m…®dorozir gumazir atrivim…®n gariba ko, atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n garir m…®dorozir gumaziba, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghuegha atrivir igiam inigha an akua atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n zuima, gumazamiziba bar men g…®n zui. Me bar ghua otivigha, tiar akar me kamagh…®n d…®borim, Tiar Akar P…®n Itim, an aven ghua Joas isava atrivir dabirabim gat…®z…® an a gapera.  
\v 21 Egha Judan gumazamiziba bar akonge. Me fo, m…®dorozir gumaziba Atalia m…®soghez…® an areme. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, gumazamiziba navir am…®rizim sara Jerusalem…®n iti. 
\c 24  
\s1 Joas uamategha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®ri 
\r (2 Atriviba 12:1-16) 
\p  
\v 1 Joas 7plan azeniba ikia, egha atrivim…®n oto. Egha 40plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. Joas…®n amebam…®n ziam Sibia, a Berseban nguibar ekiam…®n amizim.  
\v 2 God…®n ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiada ikiav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, Joas Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh ami.  
\v 3 Ez…® Jehoiada, Atrivim Joas bagha amizir pumuning ginaba. Ez…® Joas aning…®n itima, aning otariba ko guiviba bate. 
\p  
\v 4 Ez…® dughiar maba ghuegha g…®vaz…®ma, Joas uamategh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®rasa n…®ghn…®si.  
\v 5 Egha a ofa gamir gumaziba ko Livaiba akuvagha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa mang…® Judan nguibar ekiabar itir gumazamiziba bar me m…®k…®mt…®, me e uan God…®n D…®penim ak…®rs…® dag…®abar ar…®gh. Ia azenibar zurara ingangarir kam damu. Egh ia dat…®r…®gh…®n zuam…®ra mang…® dag…®ar kaba inigh.‚Äù Ez…® Livaiba zuam…®ra ingangarir kam gamizir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 6 Egha Joas g…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ko Livaibar garir gumazir dapanim Jehoiadan diagha, kamagh…®n an azara, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…® n…® Livaibar av…®raght…®, me zuam…®ra Judaba ko Jerusalemia da takis…®n dag…®aba inian aghua? Ia fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses, Israelian gumazamiziba ko, akam ak…®righa ghaze, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Purirpenim…®n ingangaribar amus…® takis…®n dag…®aba iniam.\f + \fr 24:6 \ft N…®, Ua Me Ini 30:11-16…®n gan.\f* Ez…® Livaiba tizim bagh mang…® takis…®n dag…®aba inian aghua?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Amizir kurar kam Atalia atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, an adarazi Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim akarigha aven ghuegha bizir mabagh as…®ghas…®ki. Egha me uaghan gumaziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®ngizir biziba bar ada inigha, uan asem Bal…®n ziam fasa ada inigha ghue. Kamagh…®n amiz…® Joas ingangarir kaba ua dar amuasa n…®ghn…®si. 
\p  
\v 8 Egha atrivim dag…®abar ar…®ghasa Livaibav kemez…®, me boksiar mam…®n ingari, egha me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n anet…®.  
\v 9 Egha me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim bagha takis…®n dag…®aba inigh izasa, Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba ko Judan kantrin danganiba bar dar itir darazi bagha akam amada. Israelia fom…®ra gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n itima, God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses me m…®kemez…®, me takis an…®ngiz…® mogh…®n, me dat…®r…®gh…®n ua takisbar an…®ngam.  
\v 10 Ez…® gumazir dapaniba ko gumazamiziba bar, akar kam baregha, me bar akonge. Egha me dag…®aba inigha iza boksiar kam gazuima, a bar iz…®fa.  
\v 11 Ez…® Livaiba dughiabar zurara boksiar kam…®n gari a iz…®vav…®ra itima, me a isa atrivim…®n ingangarir gumaziba bagha zui. Eght…® atrivim…®n gumazir ak…®nafariba osirim ko God…®n ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, boksiar kam…®n dag…®aba bar da inigh, egh boksiam uam a is…® an danganim dat…®gham. Me kamagh…®ra amuava, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®rasa, dag…®ar bar av…®riba ini. 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Atrivim Joas ko ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Jehoiada, dag…®ar kaba inigha, D…®penim ak…®rm…®ghamin gumazibar gumazir dapanibagh an…®ngi. Ez…® gumazir dapanir kaba ghua ingangarir gumazir kabagh ivezasa me ini. D…®penibar ingarir gumaziba ko, gumazir derav…®ra dag…®abar d…®penibar ingariba ko, gumazir derav…®ra ain ko bras…®n bizibar ingariba, me me iniz…®. Eght…® me ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ingar an anek…®ram.  
\v 13 Ingangarir gumazir kaba bar puv…®ra ingarava God…®n D…®penim bar derav…®ra anek…®riz…®, a fom…®ra ikez…® mogh…®n otogha bar deragha bar gavgafi.  
\v 14 Ingangarir gumaziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ingara aneg…®vaz…®, gol ko silvan naba ikiav…®ra iti. Ez…® ingangarir gumazibar dapaniba silva ko gol…®n kaba atrivim ko Jehoiada gan…®ngi. Eght…® aning ingangarir gumazir igharazibav kemeght…®, me silva ko gol…®n kaba inigh, ofa damuamin biziba, ko pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim tuamin itariba, ko itarir igharaziba ko baghaba, ko God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ingaramin bizir igharaziba sara ingaram. Ez…® Jehoiada ikiav…®ra itir dughiam…®n, gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghua ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribagh ami. 
\p  
\v 15 Ez…® g…®n Jehoiada bar ghuri, ez…® an azeniba 130plan tuz…®, an areme.  
\v 16 Ez…® gumazamiziba Jehoiadan ingangarir an amiziba ko arazir aghuir a God…®n damazim…®n amizibagh n…®ghn…®si. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me an kuam isa Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n itir atriviba afir danganim…®n anefa. 
\s1 Judaba ak…®rim ragha God gasara 
\p  
\v 17 Jehoiada ovegha g…®vaz…®, Judan gumazir dapaniba iza Atrivim Joas…®n ziam fava anepezeperima, a men akabar g…®n zui.  
\v 18 Atrivim Joas Juda ko Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba ko, me ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men ovavibar God gasara, egha me ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n an ziam fer puvat…®. Me guarir ak…®nir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itiba, ko marvir guabar ingarigha, dar ziaba fe. Me os…®mt…®zir bar dafam God…®n damazim…®n a gami, kamagh…®n God men an…®ngaghe.  
\v 19 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, gumazamiziba uamategh a bagh izasa, an Akar Gavgavim uan akam inigha izir gumazibav kemez…®, me ghua gumazamizibav geima, gumazamiziba men akaba baraghan aghua. 
\p  
\v 20 \x - \xo 24:20-21 \xt Matyu 23:35; Luk 11:51\x*Ez…® God…®n Duam, ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiadan otarim Sekaraia gapasa. Ez…® gumazamiziba Sekaraian ganasa, an azenim gir…®gha ghua bar me gafiragha m…®t…®gha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God kamagh…®n m…®gei: Ia an Akar Gavgaviba munasaragha g…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia deraghv…®ra ikian kogham. Ia tizim bagha arazir kam gami? Ia ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasaragha g…®fa, kamagh…®n amiz…®, an ak…®rim ragha ia gasara.‚Äù  
\v 21 Ez…® Atrivim Joas uan gumazir dapaniba ko me Sekaraian akar kabar aghuagha a m…®sueght…®, an aremeghasa akabav sosi. Egha atrivim m…®kemez…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven, gumazamiziba uari akuvir danganim…®n dag…®abar a giniva ghuav…®ra itima, an areme.  
\v 22 Atrivim Joas, a Sekaraian afeziam Jehoiada amizir arazir aghuibagh n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. A pura Sekaraia m…®soghez…® an areme. Sekaraia duam suer dughiam…®n, a kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God ia amir bizir kam…®n ganigh ia ikarvagh ivezir kuram ia dan…®ngam.‚Äù 
\s1 Me Joas m…®soghez…® an areme 
\p  
\v 23 Azenir kam g…®vaz…® azenir igiam otivasa amir dughiam…®n, Sirian kantrin m…®dorozir gumaziba iza Atrivim Joas ko m…®sosi. Me iza kantri Judan otivigha, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n m…®sogha, Joas…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba ab…®ni. Egha Siriaba men gumazir dapaniba bar me m…®soghez…®ma me ariaghire. Egha me Judabar bizir bar av…®riba inigha Damaskus…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghua, Sirian atrivim gan…®ngi.  
\v 24 Judaba ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men ovavibar God gasara, kamagh…®n amiz…®, bizir kaba otifi. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Sirian m…®dorozir gumazir b…®zir muziarim ataghiz…®, me iza Judan m…®dorozir gumazir bar av…®rim m…®sogha me ab…®ra. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, arazir kam…®n Atrivim Joas…®n arazir kuram ikarvagha ivezir kuram a gan…®ngi.  
\v 25 M…®dorozir kam…®n, Joas duar bar av…®riba ini. Ez…® m…®dorozim g…®vaz…®, Siriaba uamategha uan nguibabar ghuez…®, atrivim…®n gumazir dapanir maba, me Joas, ofa gamir gumazim Jehoiadan otarim…®n m…®soghez…®, an aremezir bizir kam g…®n…®ghn…®si. Egha me Joas amizir bizir kurar kam ikarvagh, a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa akam ak…®ri. Ez…® Joas g…®n uan dakozim…®n akuima, me an dakozim…®n a m…®soghez…®ma an areme. Ez…® an kuam, me atriviba afir danganim…®n anefazir puvat…®. Me an kuam isa, Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n anefa.  
\v 26 Atrivim m…®soghez…® an aremezir gumazimning…®n ziamning, Sabat ko Jehosabat. Sabat…®n amebam Simeat, an Amonian adarazir amizim. Ez…® Jehosabat…®n amebam Simrit, a Moapian adarazir amizim.  
\v 27 Joas…®n otaribar eghaghaniba, ko God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®ar av…®rir a gasiba, ko a uamategha God…®n D…®penim ak…®rizir eghaghaniba, da bar mogh…®ra ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n iti, Atrivibar Eghaghanibar Akar M…®ngarir Maba. Joas aremegha g…®vaz…®, an otarim Amasia an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\c 25  
\ms1 Atrivim Amasian eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 25) 
\s1 Amasia Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 14:2-6) 
\p  
\v 1 Amasia 25plan azeniba ikia, egha atrivim…®n otogha, 29plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim iti. An amebam, Jehoadin, a Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizir mam.  
\v 2 Amasia arazir aghuibara Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh amua, egha guizbang…®ra uan navir averiam…®n dar g…®nt…®zir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 3 Amasia Judan kantri gativagha gavgavigha an garir dughiam…®n, a m…®kemez…®ma, me ghua, an ingangarir gumazir dapanir an afeziam Atrivim Joas m…®soghez…® an aremezir kamning m…®soghez…® aning areme.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 25:4 \xt God…®n Araziba 24:16\x*Egha a ingangarir gumazir kamning…®n boribav soghez…®, me ariaghirezir puvat…®. A me ataghiz…®, me iti. An Ak…®nafarim…®n itir Moses Osirizir Araziba itir akabar g…®n zui. Ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven Ikiav…®ra Itir God Akar Gavgavim e gan…®ga ghaze, ‚ÄúGumazitam…®n borim arazir kuratam damight…®, ia an arazir kuram ikarvaghs…®, an amebam ko afeziam m…®sueght…®, aning aremeghan kogham. Eght…® kamagh…®ra, amebam ko afeziam arazir kuratam damight…®, ia aning…®n arazir kuram ikarvaghs…®, aning…®n boribav sueght…®, me ar…®m…®ghiran kogham. Gumazim arazir kuram damight…®, ia anar…®ra m…®sueght…®, an aremegh.‚Äù 
\s1 Amasia ghua Idomia ko m…®sosi 
\r (2 Atriviba 14:7) 
\p  
\v 5 Atrivim Amasia, Judaba ko Benjamin…®n adarazi bar men diaz…®, me iza uari akufa. Me iza uari akuvaz…®, a 20plan azeniba itir gumazir igiaba ko 20plan azenibagh afiraziba am…®sevegha, me isa uan m…®dorozir gumazibar me ar…®ki. Egha a 1,000plan m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir dapaniba, ko 100plan m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir dapaniba am…®sefe. Egha a ik…®ziba vaghvagha, men ganasa gumazir dapanir maba ar…®ki. Ez…® m…®dorozir gumazibar d…®bobonim 300,000…®n tu. Me bar mogh…®ra afuziba ko orabar suigha m…®soghan bar fo.  
\v 6 Egha a uaghan 100,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir aghuiba kantri Israel…®n ada ini. A silvabar me givese, ez…® silvan kabar os…®mt…®zim 3,000 kilogrem…®n tu. 
\p  
\v 7 Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam ghua kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúIsrael…®n kantrin gumaziba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n apengan itir puvat…®, ez…® a me ko itir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir kaba inight…® me m…®dorozim bagh n…®n g…®n mangan mark…®.  
\v 8 N…® kamagh…®n fogh, God uab…®ra gumazibar amut…®, me uan apaniba ab…®ragham, o men apaniba me ab…®ragham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, pura bizim, n…® uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba inigh m…®dorozim bagh mang…®, egh atiatingan kogh…®va bar pamtem m…®sogham. God n…®n apanibar amight…®, me n…® ab…®ragham.‚Äù\f + \fr 25:8 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® Amasia akar kam baregha kamagh…®n akam inigha izir gumazim…®n azara, ‚ÄúEz…® 3,000 kilogrem silvan k…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumazibagh ivezeziba, k…® manmagh…®n dar amuam?‚Äù 
\p Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim kamagh…®n Amasian akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúN…® n…®ghn…®zir av…®ribar amuan mark…®. Silvan dag…®ar n…® me gan…®ngizir kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God da ikarvagh bar av…®riba n…® dan…®ngam, eght…® da silvan n…® an…®ngizir kaba bar dagh afiragham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® Amasia Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir kaba amangiz…®, me uamategha uan nguibabar ghue. Ez…® me Judaba bagha naviba bar men ikufi. 
\p  
\v 11 Egha g…®n Amasia gavgavim uan n…®ghn…®zim ganigha, uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha Idomia m…®soghasa Danganir Zarir Amangs…®zir Av…®rim Itim…®n ghu. Egha me Idomian m…®dorozir gumazir 10,000pla m…®soghez…® me ariaghire.  
\v 12 Egha me ua 10,000plan gumazir igharazibar suigha me inigha m…®ghs…®ar mam…®n ghuavanabo. Egha me isava davarir bar konir mam…®n me akuniz…®, me bar m…®saraghire. 
\p  
\v 13 Amasia uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko ghua Idomia m…®sozir dughiam…®n, Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir Amasia uam amangiziba, me uamategha iza Judan nguibar ekiabav sosi, me Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ikegha ghua, Bethoron…®n nguibar ekiam…®n tu. Egha me 3,000plan gumazamizibav soghez…® me ariaghirez…®, me nguibar ekiar kabar itir bizir aghuir bar av…®riba inigha ghue. 
\s1 Akam inigha izir gumazir mam Amasian atari 
\p  
\v 14 Atrivim Amasia Idomia m…®sogha me ab…®ragha g…®vagha, men marvir guaba inigha uamategha Judan izegha, uan asebar m…®n da at…®gha, dar ziaba fasa da bagha ofan m…®n pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba tue.  
\v 15 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Atrivim Amasian arazir kam…®n ganigha bar a baseme. Egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan akam inigha izir gumazim amadaz…®ma, a ghua kamagh…®n Amasia m…®gei, ‚ÄúN…® tizim bagha ik…®zir igharazim…®n asebar ziaba fe? N…® fo, aser kaba uan adarazir akuragha n…®n dafarim…®n ua me inizir puvat…®. Ez…®, n…® tizim bagha dar ziaba fe?‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim m…®g…®av…®ra itima, Amasia an m…®g…®r…®g…®aba atugha kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúTina n…®ghn…®zim na dan…®ngasa n…® am…®sefe? N…® uan akam dukuagh. Puvat…®ght…®, k…® uan m…®dorozir gumazitam m…®kemeght…®, a n…® m…®sueght…® n…® aremegham.‚Äù 
\p Ez…® God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim uan akam dukumasa, egha ua kamagh…®n atrivim m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® dat…®r…®gh…®n fo, n…® arazir kuram gamigha, dat…®r…®gh…®n nan akam baraghan aghua. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God dat…®r…®gh…®n n…® gas…®ghas…®gham.‚Äù 
\s1 Amasia Israelia ko m…®sosi 
\r (2 Atriviba 14:8-20) 
\p  
\v 17 Ez…® g…®n Judan Atrivim Amasia, Israelian Atrivim Jehoas bagha gumaziba amangi. Atrivim Jehoas, a Joahas…®n otarim, egha Jehun igiavotarim. Gumazir kaba ghua Jehoas batogha, kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim Amasia, a Israelia, ia ko m…®soghasa m…®gei. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia iz…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Ez…® Jehoas, Judan Atrivim Amasian akam ikaragha kamagh…®n akar is…®n zuim…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúLebanon…®n kantrin aven, d…®koniba itir ikar…®zir mam, temer sidan mam bagha akam amaga kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄòN…® uan guivim, nan otarim bagh anemangasa k…® ifonge. Eght…® aning uaning…®n ikiam.‚Äô D…®koniba itir ikar…®zir kam, akar kam m…®kemez…®, g…®n as…®zir atiar mam danganir kam garua, ikar…®zir kam d…®kab…®niz…®, a ikufi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 Jehoas akar is…®n zuir kam gamua, ua kamagh…®n Amasia m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® fo, bar guizbang…®ra, n…® Idomia m…®sogha bar me ab…®ra. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® bar akuegha uan ziam bar a fe. N…® m…®dorozir kam…®n ziar ekiam ini. N…® dat…®r…®gh…®n bar akuegh, deraghv…®ra uan nguibam…®n ik…®. Egh n…® ua e m…®soghs…® m…®dorozim foran mark…®. Puvat…®ght…®ma, n…® ko Judan gumazamiziba, iregh bar ikuvigham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Ez…® Amasia Jehoas…®n akam baraghan aghua. Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Judaba Idomian asebar ziaba fe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God Judaba is…® men apanibar dafarim dar…®ghasa n…®ghnigha g…®fa.  
\v 21 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Israelian Atrivim Jehoas Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me nguibar ekiar Judan kantrin itim Betsemes…®n ghugha, Judabar Atrivim Amasia ko an m…®dorozir gumaziba ko m…®sosi.  
\v 22 Me uariv sogha ghua, Israelia Judan m…®dorozir gumaziba d…®kab…®raz…®, Judan m…®dorozir gumaziba ara ua uan nguibabar ghue.  
\v 23 Ez…® Israelian Atrivim Jehoas, Betsemes…®n nguibar ekiam…®n Judabar Atrivim Amasian suira. Amasia, Atrivim Joas…®n otarim, egha Atrivim Ahasian igiavotarim. Ez…® g…®n, Atrivim Jehoas Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, Betsemes…®n nguibar ekiam ategha Jerusalem…®n ghue. Egha me Jerusalem av…®nizir d…®vazir gavgavim gas…®ghas…®gha, Efraim…®n Tiar Akam…®n ikegha ghua, Tiar Akar M…®kebam…®n Itim…®n tu. D…®vazir kuvizir kam…®n ababanim, a 200 mitan tu. 
\p  
\v 24 Ez…® Jehoas Jerusalem…®n aven ghua, golba ko silvan nguibar ekiam…®n itiba bar ada ini. A uaghan itarir ekiaba ko itarir igharazir Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itiba, ko atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n mongezir dag…®aba bar ada ini. Egha a uaghan Obetidom ko Judan gumazir ekiar maba isa kalabuziabar m…®n me at…®gha kamagh…®n Amasia m…®gei, ‚ÄúAmasia, n…® uam Israelia e m…®soghs…® n…®ghn…®ghan mark…®. N…® kamagh…®n damight…®, k…® n…®n gumazir ekiabav sueght…®, me ar…®ghiregham.‚Äù An akar kam m…®kemegha g…®vagha, gumazir ekiar kaba ko gumazamizir maba ko bizir iniziba sara inigha ua Samarian ghu. 
\p  
\v 25 Ez…® g…®n Israelian atrivim Jehoas aremegha g…®vaz…®, Judan Atrivim Amasia ua 15plan azenibar ikegha, areme.  
\v 26 Atrivim Amasia amizir arazir igharaziba bar, a faragha atrivim…®n otozir dughiam…®n ikegha ghua an aremezir dughiam…®n eghaghaniba, ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judaba ko Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghanibar Ak…®nafarim. 
\p  
\v 27 Atrivim Amasia ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasarazir dughiam…®n, gumazir maba a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa akam ak…®ri. Ez…® an akar kam baregha, ara Lakis…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. Ez…® an apanir kaba gumazir maba amangiz…®, me an g…®n Lakis…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghua, a m…®soghez…® an areme.  
\v 28 Ez…® me an kuam inigha hoziabagh at…®gha ua Jerusalem…®n izegha, Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n, an inazir afeziaba afez…® nagh…®n anefa. 
\c 26  
\ms1 Atrivim Usian eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 26) 
\s1 Usia Judan atrivim…®n oto 
\r (2 Atriviba 14:21-22; 15:1-7) 
\p  
\v 1-2 Atrivim Amasia uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremegha g…®vaz…®ma, Judaba bar, an otarim Usia am…®sevez…®, a uan afeziam…®n danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. Usia 16plan azeniba ikiava atrivim…®n oto. An atrivim…®n itima azenir maba g…®vaz…®, a ghua m…®sogha apanibar dafaribar, ua Elat…®n nguibar ekiam ini. Egha nguibar ekiar kam…®n danganir ikuviziba, a uam adar k…®ri. 
\p  
\v 3 Usia 16plan azeniba ikia atrivim…®n oto, egha 52plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. An amebam Jekolia, a Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n amizim.  
\v 4-5 \x - \xo 26:4-5 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 24:2\x*Usia atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, gumazir mam Sekaraia, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n atiating an apengan ikiamin arazibar an sure gami. Sekaraia angam…®ra itir dughiam…®n, Atrivim Usia God baghav…®ra iti. Usian afeziam Amasia amiz…® mogh…®n, Usia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh ami. Egha Usia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ifongiam…®n g…®nt…®ghasa gavgavighav…®ra itima, God an akuraz…® bizir an amiba bar deraghav…®ram otifi. 
\p  
\v 6 Egha Atrivim Usia d…®kavigha ghua Filistiaba ko m…®sosi. Egha a me m…®sogha me ab…®ragha, Get…®n nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazim ko, Japnen nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazim ko, Asdot…®n nguibam av…®nizir d…®vazim, a bar da akaraghar…®ki. Egha a Asdot…®n nguazim ko Filistian nguazim…®n danganir igharazibar nguibar ekiar igiabar ingari.  
\v 7 God Usian akuraz…®, a Filistiaba ko Meunia ko Gurbal…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itir Arebian adarazi ab…®ni.  
\v 8 Usia atrivir bar gavgavim…®n otoz…®, kantrin mar itibar ikegha ghua Isip…®n m…®taghniam…®n tuzir gumazamiziba bar an ziar ekiam…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am barasi. Ez…® Amonia takis…®n m…®n dag…®aba a gan…®ga, uari an akakagha ghaze, me an apengan iti. 
\p  
\v 9 Egha Usia Jerusalem…®n, nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazim gavgavim a gan…®di. A tauan gavgaviba, Tiar Akar M…®kebam…®n Itim, ko Danganir Zarim…®n Zuir Tiar Akam, ko S…®ghar Konim…®n m…®n amizir d…®vazim gis…®n tauabar ingari, eght…® m…®dorozir gumaziba dar ik…® apaniba bagh ganam.  
\v 10 Atrivim Usia a bulmakauba ko sipsip…®n bar av…®riba, danganir zariba ko aruem uaghiri nagh…®n m…®ghs…®ar muziaribar iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Usia gumazamiziba puvat…®zir danganim…®n apaniba bagha garir gumaziba bagha tauan ruarir mabar ingari. Egha a uaghan an as…®ziba damasa d…®par mozir av…®ribagh kui. Usia azenibar ingarava da oparir ingangarim bar a gifonge. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a gumazamizibav kemez…®, me dagheba bar deragha otivir nguaziba ko m…®ghs…®ar dozibar, azenibar ingarigha, wain…®n ikar…®ziba ko dagher av…®rir igharazir maba saram oparigha deraghav…®ra dar gari. 
\p  
\v 11 Atrivim Usia m…®dorozir gumazir bar av…®riba iti, ez…® me m…®soghan bar fo. Ez…® atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim Jeiel, ko m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazim Masea, aning m…®dorozir gumaziba mega vaghvagha okoruar me ikiamibar me ar…®ki. Ez…® atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir faragha zuim Hanania, ingangarir kam damuasa aning…®n faragha ghua aning…®n gari.  
\v 12 Judan ik…®zibar gumazir dapaniba, me Usian m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir kabar dapanibar iti, ez…® men d…®bobonim 2,600…®n tu.  
\v 13 M…®dorozir gumazibar d…®bobonim 307,500…®n tu. Ez…® me bar gavgavigha atrivim…®n akuragh apanibav sogh me ab…®namin fofoziba iti.  
\v 14 Ez…® Atrivim Usia m…®soghamin bizir igharagha garir av…®rim ar…®ghiz…®, da iti. Bizir kaba: afuziba ko, oraba, dapanir asuaba, m…®dorozir korotiaba, barir piba ko katapel…®n asamin dag…®aba.  
\v 15 Egha a uaghan Jerusalem…®n fofozir gumazir maba iti, ez…® me katapel…®n bar dafabar m…®n masinbar ingarigha, da ar…®ghiz…® da iti. Eght…® m…®dorozim otivamin dughiam…®n, me katapel…®n m…®n garir masin…®n kaba ater nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazir m…®tiar gavgavim…®n ghuavanang, d…®vazir m…®tiar s…®ghar konim amadazir danganim gis…®n itir taua ko m…®dorozir gumaziba apaniba bagha gara itir tauan gavgavibar dar ar…®gham. Egh\f + \fr 26:15 \ft M…®dorozir masin…®n kam mati katapel…®n ekiam. Me an dag…®ar ekiaba ko afuzibar uan apanibagh as…®vamangam.\f* me masin…®n kabar afuziba ko dag…®abagh as…®vamang…®t…®, da apaniba bagh mangam. 
\p Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar deraghav…®ram Usian akurvazima, a ingangarir bar av…®ribagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Usia atrivir bar gavgavim…®n oto, ez…® saghon itir nguibar ekiabar gumazamiziba an ziar ekiam…®n akaba barasi. 
\s1 Usia God barazir puvat…® 
\r (2 Atriviba 15:5-7) 
\p  
\v 16 \x - \xo 26:16 \xt God…®n Araziba 32:15; 1 Atriviba 13:1-4\x*Atrivim Usia, bar gavgavigha uan ziam fa ifaghata ghaze, an atrivir bar gavgavim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a ir…®gha ikufi. A Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan God…®n akam…®n g…®nt…®zir puvat…®. Dughiar mam, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ghua pauran mughuriar aghuim tuer ofa gamir dakozim…®n ofa damuasa zui.  
\v 17 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazim Asaria garima, Usia aven zuima, Asaria Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir gumazir gavgavir 80pla inigha an g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven zui.  
\v 18 \x - \xo 26:18 \xt Ua Me Ini 30:7-8; D…®boboniba 3:10; 16:39-40\x*Egha me an atara kamagh…®n a m…®gei ‚ÄúAtrivim Usia, n…® oragh. Kar n…®n ingangarim puvat…®, n…® ofan mughuriar aghuim zuim Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh a damuan kogham. Ikiav…®ra Itir God ofan kabar amuasa, Aron…®n ovavir boribara am…®sefe. Merara ofa gamir gumaziba, egha me God baghav…®ra iti. N…® bar os…®mt…®zir ekiam…®n God gami, kamagh amiz…®, n…® zuam…®ra danganir kam atakigh. N…® ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Gavgavim…®n damazim…®n ziar aghuim ikian kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 19 \x - \xo 26:19 \xt 2 Atriviba 5:25-27\x*Dughiar kam…®n, Usia, pauran mughuriar aghuim otivamin itarim…®n suiragha, ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n tughav iti. An akar kam baregha, ofa gamir gumazir kabar atari. Ez…® lepan ar…®mariam zuam…®ram an m…®nedevim bato. Bizir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven, pauran mughuriar aghuim tuamin ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n, ofa gamir gumazibar damazim…®n oto.  
\v 20 God…®n ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Asaria, ko ofa gamir gumazir igharaziba garima, lepan ar…®mariam atrivim Usian m…®nedevim…®n itima, me d…®gavir kuram gamigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n an av…®raz…®ma, an azenan ghu. Ez…® a fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God an an…®ngaghegha, ar…®mariar kam gamiz…® an a bato. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a zuam…®ra azenan ghu. 
\p  
\v 21 Atrivim Usian itir Lepan ar…®mariar kam g…®vaghan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, a uamategh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven mangan kogham. Usia uaghan atrivir d…®penim ategha ghua d…®penir igharazim…®n uab…®ra iti. Ez…® an otarim Jotam, an atrivir ingangarim gamua, atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n gara, egha kantri gativagha an gara ghuav…®ra itima, Atrivim Usia areme. 
\p  
\v 22 Ez…® Atrivim Usia amizir arazir igharaziba bar, a faragha atrivim…®n otozir dughiam…®n ikegha ghua an aremezir dughiam…®n eghaghaniba, da Emos…®n otarim Aisaia, a God…®n akam inigha izir gumazim, an osirizir ak…®nafarim…®n aven iti.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 26:23 \xt Aisaia 6:1\x*Atrivim Usia uan inazir afeziabar m…®n areme. Ez…® gumaziba fo, a lepan ar…®mariam iti, kamagh…®n amiz…® me an kuam isa atriviba afir danganim…®n ghua mong saghon anefa. Ez…® an otarim Jotam, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\c 27  
\ms1 Atrivim Jotam…®n Eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 27) 
\s1 Jotam Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 15:32-38) 
\p  
\v 1 Jotam 25plan azeniba ikia atrivim…®n oto, egha 16plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. An amebam Jerusa, a Sadok…®n guivim.  
\v 2 Jotam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuiba ami, mati an afeziam Usia amiz…® mok…®n. Jotam…®n afeziam faragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ghugha arazir kuram gami. Ez…® Jotam arazir aghuim gamua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ghuzir puvat…®. Ez…® Judan gumazamiziba arazir kurabagh amua ghuav…®ra iti. 
\p  
\v 3 Ez…® Jotam m…®kemez…®, ingangarir gumaziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir D…®vazim…®n, Tiar Akar P…®n Itim…®n ingari. Egha me Jerusalem…®n aven itir danganim Ofel…®n borogh…®n, gavgavim bar d…®vazim gan…®ga ingangarir av…®ribagh ami.  
\v 4 Egha an ingangarir gumaziba, Judan anabam…®n m…®ghs…®aba itir danganibar, nguibar ekiabar ingari. Egha m…®ghs…®ar temer av…®riba itibar, me m…®dorozir gumaziba mang…® ik…® ganamin d…®penir gavgaviba ko tauan gavgavibar ingari.  
\v 5 Ez…® g…®n, Jotam uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me ghua kantri Amonian atrivim ko an m…®dorozir gumazibav sosi, egha Jotam…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba, bar me ab…®ra. Egha Jotam, Amonia m…®g…®a ghaze, ia takis na dan…®ngam. Ez…® Amonia azenir kamra 3,400plan kilogrem silva ko 1,000 tan wit ko 1,000 tan baliba isa Jotam gan…®ngi. Amonia kamagh…®ra azenir namba 2 ko namba 3…®n biziba a gan…®ngi.  
\v 6 Jotam Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan God…®n damazim…®n God ifongezir arazibagh ami. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an atrivir bar gavgavim…®n oto.  
\v 7 Ez…® bizir igharazir Jotam amizibar eghaghaniba, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n iti, Judaba ko Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghanibar Ak…®nafarim. Ak…®nafarir kam uaghan an amizir m…®doroziba ko arazibagh eghari.  
\v 8 Jotam 25plan azeniba ikia atrivim…®n oto, egha 16plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti.  
\v 9 Egha Jotam uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam inigha ghua Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n anefa. Ez…® an otarim Ahas, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\c 28  
\ms1 Atrivim Ahas…®n eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 28) 
\s1 Ahas Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 16:1-4) 
\p  
\v 1 Ahas 20pla azeniba ikia, atrivim…®n oto, egha 16plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. An ovavim Devit arazir aghuibagh ami, ez…® Ahas Devit…®n m…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh amir pu.  
\v 2 Puvat…®. A Israelian atriviba amiz…® mogh…®n arazir kurabagh ami. A ingangarir gumazibav kemez…®, me brasba inigha asem bal…®n nedazim…®n ingari.  
\v 3 Egha a uaghan arazir bar igharazim gami. A Hinom…®n Danganir Zarim…®n uan otaribav suegha, aseba bagha ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar m…®n me tue. Egha a fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n ikezir gumazamizibar arazir kurabar g…®n zui. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar men arazibar aghuagha me batuegha, nguazir kam inigha Israelia gan…®ngi.  
\v 4 Ahas m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fer danganibar zui. Danganir kaba, da uaghan m…®ghs…®ar dozibagh is…®n ikia, temer ekiabar apengan iti. Egha an aseba bagha ofabagh amua, pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba tue. 
\s1 Siriaba ko Israelia iza  // Judaba ko uariv sosi 
\r (2 Atriviba 16:5) 
\p  
\v 5-6 \x - \xo 28:5-6 \xt 2 Atriviba 16:5; Aisaia 7:1\x*Atrivim Ahas arazir kurar bar av…®ribagh ami, ez…® Judan gumazamiziba uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men ovavibar God, ak…®rim ragha a gasara. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, God Sirian atrivim ko an m…®dorozir gumaziba amangiz…®, me iza Ahas ko an m…®dorozir gumazibav sogha me ab…®ra. Egha Siriaba, Judan av…®riba inigha ghuz…®, me Damaskus…®n kalabuziabar m…®n iti. Ez…® g…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian Atrivim, a Remalian otarim Peka amadaz…®, a uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iza, Ahas uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko me m…®sogha me ab…®ra. Egha men 120,000plan m…®dorozir gumazir gavgaviba, aruer vam…®ran me m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire.  
\v 7 Ez…® Israelian m…®dorozir gumazir gavgavir mam Sikri, a Judan gumazir aruar 3pla m…®soghez…®, me ariaghire. Men ziabar kara: Atrivim Ahas…®n otarim Masea, ko atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n garir gumazim Asrikam, ko atrivim…®n g…®rara irir gumazir dapanim Elkana.  
\v 8 Israelia, Judabar namakaba, me tong men apangkuvizir puvat…®. Me Judan 200,000plan amiziba ko boriba kalabuziabar m…®n me inigha, men bizir aghuir av…®riba sara inigha Samarian nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. 
\s1 Akam inigha izir gumazim Odet, Akar Gavgavim isa Israelia gan…®di 
\p  
\v 9 Ez…® dughiar kam…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam inigha izir gumazir mam iti, an ziam Odet. Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba uamategha izir dughiam…®n, Odet ghua me batogha kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, en ovavibar God, Judabar atara, me isa ian dafaribagh at…®. Ez…® ia bar men an…®ngaghegha, me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ia amizir arazir kurar kam…®n ganigha g…®fa.  
\v 10 Egha ia uaghan dat…®r…®gh…®n Juda ko Jerusalem…®n gumazamizibar amight…®, me kalabuziabar m…®n ian ingangarir gumazir k…®niba ko ingangarir amizir k…®nibar otivasa? Manmagh…®n ami, ia ti ghaze, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n damazim…®n deraghav…®ra ikia, egha arazir kurar kam…®n uan namakabagh amigha os…®mt…®ziba iti.  
\v 11 Ia oragh. Guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar puv ian an…®ngaghegh bar puv ia damigham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n uan namakar ia kalabuzibar m…®n ar…®ghiziba ateght…®, me uamategh uan nguibabar mang…®.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Ez…® Israel…®n 4plan gumazir aruaba, me Israelian m…®dorozir gumaziba amizir arazir kam gifongezir puvat…®. Men ziabar kara: Johanan…®n otarim Asaria, ko Mesilemot…®n otarim Berekia, ko Salum…®n otarim Jehiskia, ko Hatlain otarim Amasa.  
\v 13 Ez…® 4plan gumazir aruar kaba kamagh…®n m…®dorozir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúIa kalabuziar maba inigh kagh izan mark…®. E Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh amiz…® dar os…®mt…®zim en iti. Ia arazir kurar kam uam a damight…®, arazir kam en arazir kuraba isafuraght…®, da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n mang…® bar ekevegham. Eght…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n an…®ngagharir ekiam en ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 14 M…®dorozir gumaziba akar kam baregha, kalabuziaba ko bizir me Judan iniziba inigha, gumazir aruar kaba ko Israelian damazibar da at…®gha, me ghue.  
\v 15 Ez…® 4plan gumazir aruar kaba,\f + \fr 28:15 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®. Gumazir maba ghaze, akar kaba ‚Äú4plan gumazir aruar kaba,‚Äù a deragha m…®geir puvat…®. Me kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, ‚ÄúIngangaribar garir gumazir dapaniba, gumazir aruar maba am…®sefe, ez…® men ziaba ak…®nafarir kalabuziabar garir gumazibar ziaba itir osizirir mam…®n iti.‚Äù\f* d…®kavigha kalabuziabar akurvasi. Me m…®dorozir gumaziba m…®dorozim…®n inizir korotiar maba isa, gumazamizir korotiaba puvat…®zibagh an…®ngi. Egha me daghuasa dagarir asuaba me gan…®ga, dagheba ko d…®paba me gan…®di. Egha oliv…®n borem isa marasin…®n m…®n men duabagh aghua da nosi. Egha me gumaziba ko amizir daruan gavgaviba puvat…®ziba inigha donkibagh afegha, bar mogh…®ra men akua men adarazi bagha zui. Me ghua Jerikon nguibar ekiam…®n oto, nguibar ekiar kam, det…®n temer bar av…®riba an iti. Egha Israelia me at…®gha uamategha Samarian ghu. 
\s1 Atrivim Ahas uab…®n akurvaghasa Asiriabar azangs…®si 
\r (2 Atriviba 16:7-9) 
\p  
\v 16-17 Israelia, Judabav sogha me ab…®raz…® bizir kabar g…®n, Idomia uamategha iza Judabav sogha me ab…®ra. Egha me gumazamizir maba kalabuziabar m…®n men suigha, me inigha ghu. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Atrivim Ahas gumaziba amangiz…®, me Asirian atrivim bagh mang…® an azaraght…®, a iz…® an akuragham.  
\v 18 Ez…® Filistiaba uaghan iza aruem uaghiri nagh…®n m…®ghs…®ar muziariba ko saut…®n amadaghan itir Negev…®n danganim…®n itir Judan nguibar ekiabav sosi. Egha me Judaba ab…®ragha, Betsemes…®n nguibar ekiam ko, Aijalon…®n nguibar ekiam ko, Gederot…®n nguibar ekiam ini. Egha me uaghan Sokon nguibar ekiam ko, Timna ko, Gimson nguibar ekiam, ko dar borogh…®n itir nguibar doziba sara ini. Filistiaba nguibar ekiar kaba inigha, dagh amiz…®ma da men nguibar ekiabar otifi.  
\v 19 Os…®mt…®zir Atrivim Ahas ko Judan gumazamiziba batozim…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Ahas arazir kurar bar av…®ribagh amua, da atagh…®raghasa n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®gha, ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasara. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God kantri Juda ab…®nasa, os…®mt…®zir kaba ataghiz…® da otifi.  
\v 20 Ez…® g…®n Asirian Atrivim Tiklat Pileser Judan ize, egha Ahas…®n akurazir puvat…®. A uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iza pazav…®ra Ahas gami.  
\v 21 Ez…® Ahas, Tiklat Pileser apezeperasa, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ko atrivim…®n d…®penim ko gumazir dapanibar d…®penibar itir golba ko biziba inigha a gan…®ngi. Ez…® arazir kam tong Ahas…®n akurazir puvat…®. 
\s1 Atrivim Ahas bar God ataki 
\p  
\v 22 Atrivim Ahas os…®mt…®zir av…®riba isir dughiam…®n, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. A bar ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasaragha, arazir bar kurar av…®ribagh ami.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 28:23 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 25:14; Jeremaia 44:17-18\x*A kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúSiriaba faragha m…®dorozim…®n na ab…®ra. Sirian atrivibar aseba ti Siriabar akura. Eght…® k…® da bagh ofa damut…®, da ti uaghan nan akuragham.‚Äù Egha Ahas Sirian asebar ofa gami. An arazir kabagh amima, bizir kam bang…®n os…®mt…®zir ekiaba, a ko Israelian gumazamiziba batifi.  
\v 24 Atrivim Ahas uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven itir itarir ekiaba inigha tintinibar da ab…®agharigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akaba ase. Egha an asebar ziaba fasa, Jerusalem…®n danganiba bar dar ofa gamir dakozibar ingari.  
\v 25 Judan nguibar ekiaba bar mogh…®ra, dar gumazamiziba mang…® ofan mughuriar aghuim zuibar amu asebar ziaba fasava, Ahas m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir danganibar ingari. Egha arazir kam…®n, Ahas Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an ovavibar God gamiz…®, a bar Ahas…®n an…®ngaghe. 
\p  
\v 26 Atrivim Ahas amizir arazir igharaziba bar, a faragha atrivim…®n otozir dughiam…®n ikegha ghua an aremezir dughiam…®n eghaghaniba, ak…®nafarir kam…®n itima, me kamagh…®n a d…®bori, Judaba ko Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghanibar Ak…®nafarim.  
\v 27 \x - \xo 28:27 \xt Aisaia 14:28\x*Ez…® Ahas uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me a inigha Israelian atriviba afir danganim…®n anefazir puvat…®. Me an kuam inigha Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n ghugha anefa. Ez…® an otarim Hesekia an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\c 29  
\ms1 Atrivim Hesekian eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 29--32) 
\s1 Hesekia Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 18:1-3) 
\p  
\v 1 Hesekia azenir 25pla ikia, egha atrivim…®n oto, egha 29plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n iti. An amebam Abiya, a Sekaraian guivim.  
\v 2 Hesekia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh ami, mati an ovavim Atrivim Devit amiz…® mok…®n. 
\s1 Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim gamiz…®, a ua zue 
\p  
\v 3 Hesekia atrivim…®n itima an azenir faragha zuim…®n, an iak…®nir faragha zuim…®n, a uam Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akaba kuigha, ada ak…®rasa gumazir mabav keme.  
\v 4 Egha a God…®n ofa gamir gumazir maba ko, Livain mabav kemez…®, me iza aruem anadi nagh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n, danganir gumazamiziba uari akuvim…®n uari akufa.  
\v 5 Ez…® a kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Livaiba, ia oragh! Ia bar uari is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en ovavibar God dan…®ngigh. Bizir m…®z…®r…®zir maba D…®penir kam gamiz…® a God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®, ez…® ia bar da inigh azenan mang…® da makunigh. Egh D…®penir kam damight…®, a bar zuegh, God baghv…®ra ikiam.  
\v 6 En ovaviba deragha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God…®n akam…®n g…®nt…®zir puvat…®gha an damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami. Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God ategha D…®penir a itim ak…®rim ragha a gasara.  
\v 7 Egha me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n azuarim…®n tiar akaba asegha, lam…®n isiba amunge. Egha me pauran mughuriar aghuim zuim tuer puvat…®gha, Israelian God bagha ofa gamir dakozim…®n, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribagh amir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 8-9 ‚ÄúJudaba ko, Jerusalemia arazir kurar kabagh amima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God men an…®ngaghegha me gas…®ghas…®ki. An apaniba amadaz…® me iza, en inazir afeziabav soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha me en amuiba ko, otariba ko, guiviba inigha ghua kalabuziabar m…®n uan kantrin ghue. Ez…® ik…®zir igharazibar gumazamiziba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en nguibar ekiabagh amizir biziba baregha, me d…®gavir kuram gamua, bar atiatigha d…®bovir akabar e gami. Ez…® e bizir kaba bar adagh fo. 
\p  
\v 10 ‚ÄúKamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelia en God ko Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim damuasa uan navir averiam…®n aven n…®ghn…®si, eght…® a uam en an…®ngaghan kogham.  
\v 11 Ia ofa gamir gumaziba ko Livaiba, ia kamagh…®n fogh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God uan ingangaribar amuasa ia am…®sefe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia bar derav…®ra ingangarir kam damu. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n tugh an ingangarim damuva, tuavim gumazamizibar akakaght…®, me guiz…®n an ziam fam. Eght…® ia ofan mughuriar aghuim zuibar amuam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 12 Atrivim…®n akam baraghizir Livaibar ziabar kara: Amasain otarim Mahat ko, Asarian otarim Joel, aning Kohat…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazimning. Ez…® Apdin otarim Kis, ko, Jehalelel…®n otarim Asaria, aning Merarin ik…®zim…®n gumazimning. Ez…® Siman otarim Joa ko, Joan otarim Iden, aning Gerson…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazimning.  
\v 13 Ez…® Simri ko Juel, aning Elisafan…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazimning. Ez…® Sekaraia ko Matania, aning Asap…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazimning.  
\v 14 Ez…® Jehuel ko Simei, aning Heman…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazimning. Ez…® Semaia ko Usiel, aning Jedutun ik…®zim…®n gumazimning.  
\v 15 Livain kaba d…®kavigha ghua uan adarazi batogha, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n uari zueghasa zueghamin arazim gami. Me zuegha g…®vagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akabar g…®nt…®gha, atrivim me m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim gamiz…® a ua zue.  
\v 16 Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim damut…®, a zueghasa an aven ghuegha, bizir God…®n damazim…®n zuezir puvat…®ziba, bar da inigha azenan ize. Me bizir kaba bar da inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n guam…®n borogh…®n, danganir ekiar me uari akuvim…®n ize. Ez…® Livaiba bizir kaba atera Jerusalem…®n azenan ghua, Kidron…®n fanem…®n danganir zarim giraghugha da ar…®ki.  
\v 17 Me iak…®nir faragha zuim…®n aruer farazim…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven itir biziba bar zueghamin ingangarim magh…®ram a gami. Me ingara ghua namba 8…®n aruem…®n me D…®penim…®n azuarim…®n tiar akam…®n otifi. Egha me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim an damazim…®n zueghasa, 8plan aruebar ua ingari. Iak…®nir kam…®n aruer namba 16…®n, me ingangarir kam ag…®vaz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim an damazim…®n ua zue. 
\s1 Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ofa gami 
\p  
\v 18 God…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba ingangarim ag…®vagha, ghua Atrivim Hesekian gara kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE Ikiav…®ra Iti God…®n D…®penim…®n itir biziba bar adagh amiz…®, da zuegha g…®fa. Ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar amuamin dakozim ko, an ingangarir biziba bar mogh…®ra, egha dakozir me God gan…®dir bretba ar…®zim ko, dakozim…®n ikiamin biziba, da bar mogh…®ra zue.  
\v 19 Atrivim Ahas fom…®ra ak…®rim ragha God gasara, egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itir itarir ekiaba ko, itarir doziba itir danganibar da inigha, danganir igharazibar da ar…®ghiz…®, e uam a da inigha izegha dagh amiz…®, da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ua zue. Egha e Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n da ar…®ki.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 20 Atrivim Hesekia akar kam baregha g…®vagha, bar m…®zaraghara Jerusalem…®n gumazir dapanibar diaz…®, me iza uari akufa. Me bar mogh…®ra iza uari akuvaz…®, a me inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim bagha zui.  
\v 21 Egha me 7plan bulmakaun apuriba ko, 7plan sipsip…®n apuriba ko, 7plan sipsip…®n nguziba ko, 7plan memen apuriba inigha da sara zui. Egh 7plan memen apurir kaba, me da Judan gumazamizibar arazir kuraba ko, atrivim…®n adarazir arazir kuraba ko, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven amizir arazir kuraba, bar mogh…®ra dagh n…®ghn…®gha, arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa damuam. Egha atrivim, as…®zir kabar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n dar ofa damuasa Aron…®n ovavir boribav keme.  
\v 22 Ez…® me 7plan bulmakaun apuriba faragha dav soghez…®, ofa gamir gumaziba dar ghuziba inigha ghua ofa gamir dakozim…®n da kavamangi. Ez…® me g…®n 7plan sipsip…®n apuriba ko, 7plan sipsip…®n nguzibav soghez…®, ofa gamir gumaziba dar ghuziba inigha ghua uaghan ofa gamir dakozim…®n da kavamangi.  
\v 23 Ez…® g…®n atrivim gumazir av…®riba ko tughav itima, ofa gamir gumaziba ghua arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofa bagha 7pla memen apuriba inigha izez…®, atrivim ko gumazir kaba bar uan dafariba isa memen kabagh is…®n ar…®ki. 
\p  
\v 24 Egha atrivim kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúE Israelian gumazamiziba bar, me e bagh arazir kuraba g…®n amadir ofaba ko, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar amuam.‚Äù Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ofa gamir gumaziba, Israelia bar men arazir kuraba g…®n amangamin ofaba bagha, 7plan memen kabav suegha, dar ghuziba inigha ghua ofa gamir dakozim…®n da kavamangi. 
\p  
\v 25 Atrivim Hesekia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God fom…®ra uan akam inigha izir gumazimning, Gat ko, Natan ko, Atrivim Devit gan…®ngizir Akar Gavgavim…®n g…®nt…®gha, Livaibav kemez…®, me gitaba ko, tambarinba ko, buaba inigha ghua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven tuivighav iti.  
\v 26 Livain kaba, Atrivim Devit fom…®ra ikiararangizir gitaba ko bizir igharazibar suigha tuivighav iti. Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba uan s…®ghabar suigha me ko tuivighav iti.  
\v 27 Ez…® Hesekia ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar amuasa, ofa gamir gumazibav kemez…®, me magh…®ra ofabagh amima, Livaiba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fer onger akabagh ami. Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba s…®ghabagh ivima, Livaiba Atrivim Devit at…®zir gitaba ko bizir igharazibagh ikarara ighiar aghuibagh ami.  
\v 28 Ez…® gumazamiziba bar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fema, Livaiba onger akabagh amima, ofa gamir gumaziba s…®ghabagh ivi. Me kamagh…®ram amua ghuav…®ra itima, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba isigha bar g…®fa.  
\v 29 Ofan kaba g…®vaz…®ma, Atrivim Hesekia ko, gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra, teviba ap…®righa dapaniba avigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe.  
\v 30 Ez…® Atrivim Hesekia gumazir dapaniba ko, me Atrivim Devit ko akam inigha izir gumazim Asap, aning fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fasa osirizir ighiaba bangasa Livaibav gei. Ez…® Livaiba bar akuegha ighiabagh ami. Egha me g…®n teviba ap…®righa dapaniba avigha God…®n ziam fe. 
\p  
\v 31 Ez…® Hesekia g…®n kamagh…®n gumazamizibav gei, ‚ÄúIa guizbang…®ra bar uari isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®ngi. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia an borogh…®n izam. Ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofaba, ko a m…®nabir ofaba inigh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n iz…®.‚Äù Ez…® gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra atrivim…®n akam baregha ofaba inigha izi. Ez…® marazi uan navir averiabar aven, bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofabar amuasa bar ifonge,  
\v 32 egha me 70plan bulmakaun apuriba ko, 100plan sipsip…®n apuriba ko, 200plan sipsip…®n nguziba inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofan kabar amuasa izi.  
\v 33 Egha me uaghan 600plan bulmakaun apuriba ko, 3,000plan sipsipba ofabar m…®n da inigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngasa izi.  
\v 34 Ofa gamir gumazir God…®n damazim…®n zueghamin arazim gamiziba av…®rasemezir puvat…®, ez…® ofan bar isi m…®gh…®ramiba bagh as…®zibav sogh, dar inibav sa da aghoramin ingangarim bar ekefe. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ingangarim zuam…®ra g…®vaghasa, Livain maba d…®kavigha ofa gamir gumazibar akuragha as…®zibav soke. Bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim kamak…®n, Livaiba faragha d…®kavigha, zuam…®ra God…®n damazim…®n zueghamin arazim…®n uarigh amigha zue. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir av…®riba zuam…®ra arazir kam gamizir puvat…®. Egha g…®n ofa gamir gumaziba God…®n damazim…®n uari zuezir arazim gamiz…®, Livaiba ua ingangarir kam gamir puvat…®.  
\v 35-36 Ofa gamir gumaziba bar, ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rir av…®ribagh ami. Egha me ingangarir kamnagh…®ram amizir puvat…®. Me God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofaba bagh as…®zibar oviba tuava, bar isia m…®gh…®rir ofaba bagha gumazamiziba inigha izezir wainba isa ofan m…®n da inge. Atrivim Hesekia uan gumazamiziba ko kamagh…®n fo, God men akuraz…® D…®penim ak…®raghasir ingangarir kaba zuam…®ra g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me God p…®rafa bar akonge. Egha me kamagh…®ra ua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ofabagh amua an ziam fe. 
\c 30  
\s1 Me, God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam damuamin biziba ak…®ri 
\p  
\v 1 Atrivim Hesekia, a God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam damuasava Israel ko, Judan gumazamiziba bagha akam amada, eght…® me iz…® Jerusalem…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n uari akuvagham. Egha a uaghan Efraim ko, Manasen anabamning…®n gumazamiziba bagha ak…®nafariba amangi.  
\v 2-3 \x - \xo 30:2-3 \xt D…®boboniba 9:9-11\x*Me iak…®nir faragha zuim…®n isar kam damuasa ifonge, mati me bar fom…®ra ami mok…®n. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir av…®riba God…®n damazim…®n zueghamin arazibagh amizir puvat…®, egha uaghan gumazamiziba iza Jerusalem…®n uari akuvazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim uan gumazir dapaniba ko, an gumazamiziba, me iak…®nir namba 2…®n isam damuasa akam ak…®ri.  
\v 4 Atrivim ko gumazamiziba bar n…®ghn…®zir kam bagha navir vam…®ra iti.  
\v 5 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me bar Israel…®n itir danganiba bagha akaba amangi. Me Berseban nguibar ekiar saut…®n amadaghan itim…®n ikegha ghua, Dan…®n nguibar ekiar not…®n amadaghan itim…®n tu. Egh gumazamizibav kemeght…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelian God bagh iz…®, Jerusalem…®n uari akuvagh God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam damuam. Moses Osirizir Araziba ghaze, Israelia bar mogh…®ra uari akuvagh isar kam damuam, ez…® men varazira arazir kam…®n g…®nt…®si. 
\p  
\v 6 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, atrivim uan gumazir dapaniba ko, ak…®nafariba osirigha gumazir mabagh an…®ga kamagh…®n me m…®g…®a ghaze, ia ak…®nafarir kaba inigh bar mogh…®ra Israel ko Judan danganiba bar dar mang…®. Ak…®nafarir kabar itir akaba kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúIa Israelian ikiav…®ra itir varazira, Asirian atriviba ia gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®ziba, ia oragh. Ia uamategh Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a en ovaviba Abraham, Aisak ko, Jekop…®n God, a bagh iz…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God iz…® ia ko ikiam.  
\v 7 Ian inazir afeziaba ko, aveghbuaba amiz…® mogh…®n, ia arazir kurabar amuan mark…®. Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a men ovavibar God, me ak…®rim ragha a gasara, ez…® God me ategha puv me gamua bar me gas…®ghas…®ki. Ez…® ia uari bizir kabar gani.  
\v 8 Ia uan ovavibar m…®n akaba batoghan mark…®. Ia uari is…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God dan…®ngigh. Egh ia Jerusalem…®n iz…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en God zurara ikiasa ua bagha m…®sevezir d…®penim…®n an ziam f…®. Ia kamagh…®n damut…®, a ua ian an…®ngaghan kogham.  
\v 9 Ia fo, ian apaniba ian aveghbuaba ko, boriba inigha uan nguibabar ghuegha, me isa kalabuziabar m…®n me ar…®ki. Ia uamategh Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagh iz…®t…®, a ian apanibar amut…®, me ian adarazir apangkuvigh, ua me amadaght…® me uamategh ian nguazim…®n izam. Bar guizbang…®ra, Ikiav…®ra Itir God ian God, a God…®n apangkuvim itim. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia navibagh iragh, a bagh uamategh iz…®t…®, a ragh ua ian gan…®va, ua ia iniam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 Ez…® gumazir kaba ak…®nafarir kaba inigha ghua Efraim…®n anabam ko, Manasen anabam…®n nguazimning…®n itir nguibar ekiabar ikegha ghua, Sebulun…®n anabam…®n nguazir not…®n amadaghan itim…®n tu. Egha me atrivim…®n akabar gumazamizibav geima, gumazamiziba oraghan aghuagha, aka m…®k…®rvagha, d…®bovir akabar gumazir kabav gei.  
\v 11 Ez…® Aser ko, Manase ko, Sebulun…®n anababar gumazir varazira akar kam baregha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n uari ab…®ragha Jerusalem…®n ghue.  
\v 12 Ez…® God uab…® Judabagh amima, me navir vam…®ra inigha bar mogh…®ra atrivim ko, an gumazir dapanibar akam…®n g…®nt…®gha iza Jerusalem…®n uari akuvagha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar Gavgaviba m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, isar kam gami. 
\s1 Me God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam gami 
\p  
\v 13 Egha iak…®nir namba 2…®n, Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam…®n, gumazamizir bar av…®rir dafam iza Jerusalem…®n uari akufa.  
\v 14 Egha me ghua Jerusalem…®n itir asebar ziaba fer ofa gamir dakoziba ko, ofan m…®gharir mughuriar aghuim zuir ofa gamir dakoziba akaraghar…®ki. Egha me ofa gamir dakozir kabar oteviba inigha, ghua Kidron…®n Fanem…®n danganir zarim…®n da makuni.  
\v 15 Egha namba 2…®n iak…®nim…®n, an aruer namba 14…®n, me God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam bagha sipsip…®n nguzibav soke. Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba, God…®n damazim…®n zueghamin arazibar g…®n ghua uari zuezir puvat…®, kamagh…®n me bar aghumsigha ghua uari zueghamin arazim…®n uarigh amigha zue. Me uari zuegha g…®vagha, ofan bar isi m…®gh…®ramibar as…®ziba inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n zui. 
\p  
\v 16 Ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba, God…®n ingangarir gumazim Moses me gan…®ngizir Arazibar g…®n ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n gumazamizibar damazim…®n tuifi. Ez…® Livaiba ofabar ghuziba inigha ofa gamir gumazibagh an…®ngiz…®, me da isa ofa gamir dakozim…®n da kavamadi.  
\v 17 Gumazamizir av…®riba, God…®n damazim…®n uari zueghasa zueghamin arazim gamizir puvat…®, kamagh…®n me uari uan sipsip…®n nguzibav suegh dar ofa damuan kogham. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Livaiba gumazamizir kabar sipsip…®n nguzibav soghez…® da Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n bizibaram otifi.  
\v 18-19 Ez…® gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra ofa gamizir sipsip…®n kabar tuziba ame. Egha me Moses Osirizir Araziba m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, men bar av…®rim faragha God…®n damazim…®n uari zuezir arazim gamizir puvat…®. Zuezir puvat…®zir gumazamizir av…®rir kabar maba, me Efraim ko, Manase ko Isakar ko, Sebulun…®n anababar adarazir ize. Atrivim Hesekia me g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n God ko m…®gei, ‚ÄúO Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en ovavibar God, n…® fo, gumazamizir kaba n…®n Arazibar g…®n ghua uari zuezir puvat…®gha, n…®n D…®penim…®n ize. Me bar ifongiar ekiam n…®n ikia n…® bagh iz…® n…®n ziam fasa. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, n…® bar dera, n…® gumazamizir kabar arazir kuraba g…®n amadagh.‚Äù  
\v 20 Ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God Hesekian azangs…®zim baregha, gumazamizir kabar arazir kuraba g…®n amadagha, me gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 21 Ez…® gumazamiziba, Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam bagha Jerusalem…®n uari akuvagha 7plan aruebar ikia bar akonge. Ez…® Livaiba ko, ofa gamir gumaziba, dughiabar zurara Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n pamtem…®n gitabav sogha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fe.  
\v 22 Isar kam…®n dughiam…®n, Livain maba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ingangariba bar deraghav…®ra dagh ami, kamagh…®n amiz…®, Atrivim Hesekia me m…®nabagha gavgavim me gan…®dir akabar me m…®gei. Dughiar kam…®n, gumazamiziba 7plan aruebar Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fer isar ekiam gamua God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofabagh amua, egha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men ovavibar God…®n ziam fava a m…®nabi. 
\s1 Me God…®n ziam fer dughiam ua 7plan aruebagh isafura 
\p  
\v 23 Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isar Ekiam…®n Dughiam…®n aruer 7pla g…®fa, ez…® gumazamiziba God…®n ziam fasa 7plan arueba ua dagh isafuraghasa akam ak…®ri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me ua 7plan aruebar God…®n ziam fa bar akongegha iti.  
\v 24 Ez…® Atrivim Hesekia 1,000plan bulmakaun apuriba ko, 7,000plan sipsipba inigha ofabar amuasa gumazamizibagh an…®ngi. Ez…® an gumazir dapaniba, 1,000plan bulmakaun apuriba ko, 10,000plan sipsipba ofabar amuasa gumazamizibagh an…®ngi. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n, ofa gamir gumazir bar av…®riba, God…®n damazim…®n uari zueghasa zueghamin arazim gami.  
\v 25-26 Ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba ko, Judan gumazamiziba ko, not…®n amadaghan Israel…®n nguazim…®n izeziba ko, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizir Juda ko Israel…®n itiba, me bar mogh…®ra Jerusalem…®n ikia bar akonge. Bar guizbang…®ra, Devit…®n otarim Atrivim Solomon…®n dughiam…®n ikegha iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, bizir kamagh…®n garitam Jerusalem…®n otozir puvat…®.  
\v 27 Ez…® g…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba d…®kavigha tuivigha deragh gumazamizibar amuasa, God…®n azangs…®si. Ez…® God uan Nguibam…®n ikia, egha uan ofa gamir gumazibar azangs…®zim barasi. 
\c 31  
\s1 Hesekia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ingangariba ak…®ri 
\p  
\v 1 God…®n ziam fer dughiar ekiar kaba g…®vaz…®ma, gumazamizir iza Jerusalem…®n uari akuvaziba, me tintinibar Judan nguibar ekiabar ghua, dag…®ar guarir ak…®niba ap…®ragharigha, temer guarir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itiba okaghar…®ki. Me uaghan Judan anabam ko, Benjamin…®n anabam ko, Manasen anabam ko, Efraim…®n anabam…®n nguazibar ghua, ofa gamir dakoziba ko, m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir danganir asebar ziaba feba saram as…®ghasigha, bizitam ataghizir puvat…®. Egha me g…®n uamategha uan nguibabar zui. 
\p  
\v 2 Atrivim Hesekia ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba tuiragha, men ik…®ziba vaghvagh damuamin ingangaribar me ar…®gha, me m…®g…®a ghaze, ia ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livain ik…®ziba fom…®ra ingariz…® mogh…®n ia ingangaribar amu. Ingangarir kaba: Me ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba ko, God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofabagh amua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®nabava, an ziam fava, an D…®penim…®n ingangariba bar dagh ami.  
\v 3 \x - \xo 31:3 \xt D…®boboniba 28:1--29:39\x*Atrivim kamagh…®n m…®g…®a ghaze, ofa gamir gumaziba, an d…®vazim…®n aven an as…®zibar tong…®n as…®ziba iniva ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba, zurara m…®zaraziba ko, guarat…®zibar dar amu. Egh me uaghan Sabat…®n dughiaba ko, iak…®nir igiaba ko, God…®n ziam fer dughiar ekiaba sara, me an as…®ziba inigh ofa damu, mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Arazir Moses fom…®ra osiriziba m…®kemez…® mok…®n. 
\p  
\v 4 \x - \xo 31:4-5 \xt D…®boboniba 18:12-13; 18:21\x*Egha atrivim kamagh…®n Jerusalem…®n gumazamizibav g…®a ghaze, me uan daghebar tong…®n daghetaba inigh ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba bagh da inigh iz…®. Gumazamiziba kamagh…®n damut…®, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba deragh uan ingangarim damuam, mati Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Araziba m…®kemez…® mok…®n.  
\v 5 Atrivim…®n akar kam, kantrin danganiba bar dar ghu, ez…® gumazamiziba zuam…®ra wit…®n faragha otivizir bar aghuiba ko, wain…®n d…®par bar av…®riba ko, oliv…®n boreba ko, haniba, ko, dagher guar av…®rir me azenibar iniziba inigha, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba bagha da inigha izi. Me uaghan uan dagheba 10plan pozibav k…®nigha, dar pozir vam…®ra isa ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaibagh an…®ngi.  
\v 6 Ez…® Judan nguibar ekiabar itir gumazamiziba, me bar mogh…®ra vaghvagha uan bulmakauba ko, sipsipba 10plan okoruabar da arigha, egha dar okoruar mam inigha zui. Me uaghan uan biziba 10plan pozibav k…®nigha, dar pozir vam…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God bagha da ar…®ki,\f + \fr 31:6 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* egha me bizir kaba bar ada inigha iza pozir av…®ribav k…®ni. 
\p  
\v 7 Gumazamiziba iak…®nir namba 3…®n, bizibar pozibav k…®nigha, da atera zui. Me kamagh…®ra amua ghua namba 7…®n iak…®nim…®n tu.  
\v 8 Ez…® Atrivim Hesekia ko, gumazir dapaniba ghua, gumazamiziba inigha izezir bizibar pozibar ganigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ziam fa, Israelian gumazamiziba m…®nabagha, me bagha bar akonge.  
\v 9 Egha atrivim kamagh…®n ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaibar azai, ‚ÄúManmagh…®n amiz…® ia dagher pozir av…®rir kaba iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 10 \x - \xo 31:10 \xt Malakai 3:10\x*Ez…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Asaria, a Sadok…®n adarazir mav, a kamagh…®n atrivim…®n akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God bar deraghav…®ra uan gumazamizibagh amiz…®, me dagher bar av…®rim inigha an D…®penim…®n ize. E dagher kabar av…®rim ame, egha da ag…®van iburaz…®, dagher pozir bar av…®riba ikiav…®ra iti.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 11 Ez…® atrivim m…®kemez…®, ingangarir gumaziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven, biziba ar…®ghasa danganiba ak…®ra dar ingari.  
\v 12 Egha me dagher kaba ko, bizir igharaziba ko, 10plan pozibar ar…®ghizir bizir kabar pozir mam inigha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n biziba ar…®ghamin danganir kabagh ar…®ki. Ez…® Livain mam…®n ziam Konania, a ingangarir kam…®n garir gumazir dapanim, ez…® an aveghbuam Simei, a ingangarir kam…®n garir gumazir namba 2.  
\v 13 Atrivim Hesekia ko, God…®n D…®penim…®n ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Asaria, aning Konania ko, Simein akurvaghasa, ua Livain maba am…®sefe. Men ziabar kara: Jehiel, Asasia, Nahat, Asahel, Jerimot, Josabat, Eliel, Ismakia, Mahat ko Benaia.  
\v 14 Imnan otarim Kore, a Livain mav, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aruem anadi nagh…®n itir tiar akam…®n garir gumazim. Atrivim ko, Asaria ingangarir kaba Kore gan…®ngi: A gumazamiziba uan ifongiabar g…®n ghua, God gan…®dir ofaba iniam. Egh uaghan ofan igharazir gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God gan…®diba inigh, ofan bar anogoroghezibar naba inigh, da tuiragh ofa gamir gumazibar an…®ngam.  
\v 15 Ez…® Livain maba Koren akurvagha ingangarir aghuim gamua, ofa gamir gumazibar nguibar ekiabar aven ingara ofa gamir gumazibar ik…®ziba bagha dagheba tuiragha me gan…®di. Livain kabar ziabar kara: Iden, Miniamin, Jesua, Semaia, Amaria ko Sekania. Me dagheba isa men ik…®ziba bar me gan…®dima, tav daghetam…®n otevezir puvat…®, me bar mogh…®ra dagheba ini, gumazir igiaba ko, ghuriba sara.  
\v 16 Ofa gamir gumazibar otariba, 3plan azeniba ik…®t…®, me men ziaba is…®va ik…®zibar ziabar apengan da osiram. Egh me daghebar an…®ngamin dughiam…®n, me ziar kabar gan…®va, dagheba me dan…®ngam. Egh God…®n ofa gamir gumazitam…®n ik…®zim mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ingaramin dughiam otoght…®, me Jerusalem…®n mangegh ingart…®, me ua men nguibam…®n me bagh daghebar ar…®ghan kogham.\f + \fr 31:16 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\p  
\v 17 Me ofa gamir gumazibar ziaba osirir dughiam…®n, me men ik…®zibar ziabar apengan da osiright…®, me uari akuvagh, uaghara ingaram. Egh Livaibar ziaba osirir dughiam…®n, me 20plan azenibar ikegha ghuanadir gumaziba, me men ik…®ziba damuamin ingangaribar apengan men ziaba osiri.  
\v 18 Egha ofa gamir gumazibar ziabar apengan, me men amuiba ko, borir iririviba ko, otariba ko, guivir asebar ziaba saram osiri. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazir kaba, zurazurara Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n uari uari zuamin ingangarim iti.\f + \fr 31:18 \ft Hibrun akam deragha akar kam…®n m…®ngarim ab…®ghizir puvat…®.\f* 
\v 19 Aron…®n adarazir ofa gamir gumazir maba, me ofa gamir gumazibar nguibar ekiabar nguazir otevir mabar iti. Ez…® gumazir maba nguibar ekiar kabar ikiava, dagheba ofa gamir gumazir kabagh an…®di. Egha me uaghan dagheba isa Livain ziabar apengan itir Livaibagh an…®di. 
\p  
\v 20 Hesekia, Judan danganiba bar dar ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaibar akurvazir ingangarir aghuim gami. Egha a Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan God…®n damazim…®n, arazir aghuiba ko, guiz…®n arazibagh ami.  
\v 21 Hesekia uan navir averiam…®n aven God baghav…®ra ikiasa bar gavgafi. Egha deraghav…®ra ingara God…®n D…®penim uam anek…®righa God…®n Akar Gavgaviba ko, an Arazibar g…®n zui. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Hesekia amizir ingangarir av…®riba, da bar deraghav…®ram otifi. 
\c 32  
\s1 Asiriaba Jerusalemia m…®soghasa izi 
\r (2 Atriviba 18:13-37; 19:14-29; 19:35-37; Aisaia 36:1-22; 37:8-38) 
\p  
\v 1 Atrivim Hesekia guizbang…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akabar g…®n ghua amizir ingangarir kabar g…®n, Asiriabar Atrivim Senakerip uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iza Judabav sosi. Egha men nguibar ekiar d…®vazir bar gavgaviba av…®niziba okarigha iti. Senakerip nguibar ekiar kabagh ativagh dar ganasa n…®ghn…®si.  
\v 2 Ez…® Hesekia kamagh…®n oraki, Senakerip uaghan Jerusalem ko m…®soghasa.  
\v 3 Ez…® Hesekia uan gumazir dapaniba ko, m…®dorozir gumazir bar gavgaviba ko, me nguibar ekiam…®n azenan itir em…®m…®rir d…®paba ap…®rasa akam m…®soke. Ez…® me bar an akura.  
\v 4 Dughiar kam…®n, me gumazir b…®zir ekiam akuvagha, kamagh…®n me m…®gei, ‚ÄúE mang…® nguibar ekiam…®n azenan itir em…®m…®rir d…®paba ap…®rika. E kamagh…®n damight…®, Asiriaba ua iz…® damamin d…®par av…®riba ikian kogham.‚Äù Egha me ghua faner men nguazim abigha zuim ko, em…®m…®rir d…®par kaba bar ada apemegha da ap…®ri. 
\p  
\v 5 Egha Hesekia zuam…®ra Jerusalem av…®nizir d…®vazim gavgavim a dan…®ngasa, uan ingangarir gumazibav gei. Ez…® ingangarir gumaziba d…®vazir akaraghirezir akuar mam uam anek…®righa, me m…®dorozir gumaziba is…®n ik…® apaniba bagh ganasa, tauan gavgavir ruariba d…®vazim gis…®n dar ingari. Egha nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazim, an azenan, me ua d…®vazir gavgavir igharazir mam…®n ingariz…®, a bar nguibar ekiam ek…®aru. Egha me Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n itir danganir zarir me nguazibar apemezim, me ua gavgavim d…®vazim gan…®di. Egha me m…®soghasa afuziba ko, orar av…®ribar ingari. 
\p  
\v 6 Egha g…®n, Hesekia Jerusalem…®n gumazamizibar ganasa, m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir dapanim am…®sefe. Egha a nguibar ekiam…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n uari akuvir danganir ekiam…®n, bar gumazamiziba akufa. Egha gavgavim men navibar an…®ngasa, akar bar aghuibar me m…®gei. A kamagh…®n me m…®gei,  
\v 7 \x - \xo 32:7 \xt God…®n Araziba 31:6; 2 Atriviba 6:16; 2 Eghaghaniba 20:15\x*‚ÄúIa tugh gavgavigh, Asirian atrivim ko, an m…®dorozir gumazir b…®zir kam…®n atiatingan mark…®. Me gavgavir bar ekiam ti, ez…® e ko itir gumazir mam, an gavgavim bar ekevegha men gavgavim bar a gafira.  
\v 8 \x - \xo 32:8 \xt Jeremaia 17:5; Rom 8:31; 1 Jon 4:4\x*Asirian atrivim, a gumaziba da uan gavgavim ini, ez…® en gavgavim, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God, en Godra. A e ko ik…® en akuragh, en m…®dorozibar aven, an e bagh en apaniba ab…®nam.‚Äù Gumazamiziba atrivim…®n akaba barazima, akar kaba gavgavim men navibagh an…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 9 Dughiar kam…®n Senakerip uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko, me Lakis…®n nguibar ekiam…®n m…®sosi. Egha a uan gumazir dapanir maba amangiz…®, me an akabar gun Hesekia ko, Judabav k…®masa Jerusalem…®n ghue. An akabar kara:  
\v 10 ‚ÄúK…® Asirian Atrivim Senakerip, k…® foghasa, ia manmagh…®n garir gavgavim ikia ghaze, e ian nguibar ekiam inian iburagham? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 11 K…® fo, Hesekia kamagh…®n ia m…®gei, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a ian God, a ian akuraght…®, e Asiriaba ia gas…®ghasighan kogham. Hesekia ia gifari, ia n…®ghn…®zir gavgavim an akabar ik…® e ateght…®, e ian nguibar ekiam inigham koght…®, ia uari bagh ganigh. E ia ek…®arught…®, ia damamin dagheba ko, d…®paba puvat…®gh ar…®ghiregham.  
\v 12 Ia fo, Hesekian kamra, m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir danganir God…®n ziam feba ko, an ofa gamir dakozir pura tintinibar itiba bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki. Egha ghaze, ia Judaba ko Jerusalemia, ia mang…® ofa gamir dakozir vam…®ra, mughuriar aghuim zuir ofabar amuva God…®n ziam fam. 
\p  
\v 13 ‚ÄúK…® uan ovaviba ko, e kantrin igharazibagh amizir biziba, ia ti dagh fozir puvat…®? Ia ghaze, igharaz darazir aseba men akuraz…®, k…® ti men kantribagh as…®ghas…®ghizir pu? Bar puvat…®.  
\v 14 E kantrin av…®riba ko m…®soke, ez…® men aser av…®riba iti. Ez…® kantrin igharazitam…®n asetam men akuraz…®, me m…®dorozir tam…®n e ab…®razir puvat…®. Ez…® ia tizim bagha ghaze, ian God ian akuraght…® ia m…®dorozim…®n e ab…®ragham? Ti puvat…®gham!  
\v 15 Ia Hesekia ateght…® a ia gifaran mark…®, egh ia an akam baraghan mark…®. Bar guizbang…®ra, kantrin igharazitam…®n asetam an akuragha gavgavim a gan…®ngiz…®, a nan ovaviba ko m…®sogha me ab…®razir puvat…®. Bar guizbang…®ra, ian God uaghan ian akuraghan kogham.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 16 Asirian atrivim…®n gumazir dapaniba, akar kurar bar av…®ribar Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko, an ingangarir gumazim Hesekia gami.  
\v 17 Atrivim Senakerip uaghan ak…®nafariba osira Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God d…®pofi. Ak…®nafarir kaba, m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kaba iti, ‚ÄúK…® kantrin igharazibav sozima, men aseba men akuraz…®, me na ab…®razir puvat…®. Ez…® kamagh…®ra, Hesekian God uaghan nan dafarim da, uan gumazamizibar akuraghan kogham. Bar puvat…®gham.‚Äù  
\v 18 Asirian gumazir dapaniba pamtem…®n Hibrun akam…®n d…®m tiariba akar m…®k…®mt…®, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam av…®nizir d…®vazir m…®tiar gavgavim gis…®n itir gumazamiziba uan akam baregh, bar atiatigham. Eght…® tuavir kam…®n, Asiriaba nguibar ekiam inian iburaghan kogham.  
\v 19 Asiriaba kamagh…®n n…®ghn…®gha ghaze, Jerusalem…®n God ti kantrin igharazibar asebar m…®n gari. Aser kaba gumazamiziba uari uan dafaribar dar ingari, kamagh…®n amiz…®, me d…®bovir akabar a gami. 
\p  
\v 20 Atrivim Hesekia, Asiriabar akar kaba baregha, akam inigha izir gumazim Aisaia ko, aning uaning…®n akurvaghasa God ko m…®g…®a an dei. (Aisaia, a Emos…®n otarim.)  
\v 21 \x - \xo 32:21 \xt 2 Atriviba 19:35\x*Ikiav…®ra Itir God aning…®n d…®mdiam baregha ensel…®n mam amadaz…®, a Asirian atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba itir danganim…®n ghua, gumazir dapaniba ko, m…®dorozir gumazir bar gavgaviba ko, m…®dorozir gumazibar garir gumazir dapanibav soghez…® me bar ariaghire. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Atrivim Senakerip bar aghumsigha, uamategha uan kantrin ghu. Egha g…®n, a uan asem…®n ziam fasa, an d…®penim…®n aven ghuz…®, an otarir maba iza m…®dorozir sababar a m…®soghez…®, an areme. 
\p  
\v 22 Arazir kam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Atrivim Hesekia ko, Jerusalemian akura, ez…® Asirian Atrivim Senakerip me gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God uaghan, igharaz darazi ataghiz…®, me iza Judabagh as…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. Judaba amir biziba bar, Ikiav…®ra Itir God men akuraz…® me navir am…®rizim sara deraghav…®ra ikia avughsi.  
\v 23 Ez…® Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamizir av…®rim, Jerusalem…®n iza, Ikiav…®ra Itir God bagha ofaba inigha izi. Me uaghan bizir aghuiba inigha iza Hesekia gan…®di. Dughiar kam…®n ikegha zui, Kantrin Igharazibar Gumazamiziba, ziar ekiam Judan Atrivim Hesekia gan…®ga ghuav…®ra iti. 
\s1 Hesekia ar…®mariam ini 
\r (2 Atriviba 20:1-3; 20:12-19; Aisaia 38:1-3; 39:1-8) 
\p  
\v 24 Asiriaba paza Judabagh amir dughiar kam…®n, Atrivim Hesekia ar…®mariar bar ekiam inigha aremeghasava ami. Dughiar kam…®n, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God ko m…®geima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God an d…®mdiam ikaragha, ababanir mam an akagha ghaze, an ar…®mariam g…®vagham.  
\v 25 \x - \xo 32:25 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 24:18; 26:16; Onger Akaba 116:12\x*Hesekian ar…®mariam g…®n g…®vaz…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an akurazir bizir ekiar kam g…®n…®ghn…®zir puvat…®. A uab…® fava, Ikiav…®ra Itir God m…®nabazir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God an an…®ngaghegha, a ko, Juda ko, Jerusalem…®n gumazamizibagh as…®ghas…®ghasava ami.  
\v 26 \x - \xo 32:26 \xt 2 Atriviba 20:19; Jeremaia 26:18-19\x*Ez…® Hesekia Jerusalemia ko, me uari fer arazim ategha uari ab…®ra. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, an atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me gas…®ghas…®ghizir puvat…®. 
\s1 Hesekia ziar ekiam ko dag…®ar bar av…®riba iti 
\p  
\v 27 Hesekia dag…®ar bar av…®riba ikia, atrivir bar gavgavim…®n otogha ziar ekiam iti. A ingangarir gumazamizibav kemez…®, me silvaba ko, gol ko, dag…®ar ivezir bar p…®n koziba ko pauran mughuriar aghuim zuiba ko, bizir igharazir ivezim bar p…®n kozibar ar…®ghamin d…®penibar ingari.  
\v 28 Ez…® an ingangarir gumaziba uaghan witba ko, wain…®n d…®paba ko, oliv…®n boreba ar…®ghamin d…®penibar ingari. Egha me uaghan bulmakaun guar av…®riba ar…®ghamin d…®penir ekiabar ingarigha, sipsipbar ar…®ghasa d…®vazibar ingari.  
\v 29 God bizir aghuir bar av…®riba Hesekia gan…®ngi, ez…® Hesekia sipsipba ko, bulmakaun bar av…®riba ini. Ez…® an ingangarir gumaziba a bagha nguibar ekiar av…®ribar ingari.  
\v 30 Atrivim Hesekia fom…®ra Gihon…®n Em…®m…®rir D…®pam p…®n anep…®righa, Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam…®n aruem uaghiri nagh…®n, d…®pam bagha nguazim…®n aven torir ruarim g…®kuiz…®, d…®pam an aven uaghiri. Atrivim Hesekia amizir biziba bar derav…®ram otifi.  
\v 31 Babilon…®n kantrin itir gumazir aruaba, God kantri Juda gamizir mirakel…®n kam…®n\f + \fr 32:31 \ft Mirakel…®n kam, an eghaghanim, a 2 Atriviba 20:8-11…®n iti.\f* eghaghanim baregha, bizir kam…®n m…®ngarim g…®foghasa gumazir maba amangiz…®, me Hesekia bagha izi. God Hesekian araziba ko, navir averiam g…®foghasa a badava, dughiar kam…®n Hesekia ataki. 
\s1 Atrivim Hesekia areme 
\r (2 Atriviba 20:20-21) 
\p  
\v 32 Atrivim Hesekia amizir bizir igharaziba ko, an arazir aghuibar eghaghaniba bar, ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n iti, Akam Inigha Izir Gumazim Aisaia, A Emos…®n Otarim, a Irebam…®n M…®n Garir Bizim…®n Ganizir Bizibar Eghaghaniba ko, ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim, Judaba ko Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghanibar Ak…®nafarim.  
\v 33 Atrivim Hesekia uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me an kuam isa Atrivim Devit…®n ovavir boribar mozibar borogh…®n anefa. An mozim atrivir igharazir mabar mozibar mong m…®ghs…®am…®n p…®n iti. Ez…® Juda ko, Jerusalemian gumazamiziba, an ziar ekiam g…®n…®ghn…®gha bar an kuarkufi. Ez…® an otarim Manase an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\c 33  
\ms1 Atrivim Manasen eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 33) 
\s1 Manase Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 21:1-9) 
\p  
\v 1 Manase azenir 12pla ikia, Judabar atrivim…®n otogha, 55plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike.  
\v 2 \x - \xo 33:2 \xt God…®n Araziba 18:9; 2 Eghaghaniba 28:3; Jeremaia 15:4\x*Manase arazir aghuim…®n g…®n zuir pu. Puvat…®. A gumazamizir igharazir fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n ikezibar arazir m…®z…®r…®zir kurabar g…®n zuima, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me batuegha, nguazir kam isa Israelia gan…®ngi. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Manase Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kabagh ami, kar arazir God…®n damazim…®n derazir puvat…®ziba. 
\p  
\v 3 Fom…®ra an afeziam Hesekia m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itir asebar ziaba fer danganiba ap…®raghar…®ki. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n, Manase ua dar ingari. Egha asem Bal…®n ziam fasa ofa gamir dakozibar ingari. Egha an aser amizim Aseran nedazim itir temer guarir ak…®nibar ingari. Egha uaghan overiam…®n itir m…®kovezibar ziaba fe.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 33:4 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 6:6\x*Egha an aseba bagha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ofa gamir dakozibar ingari. E bar fo, fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan D…®penir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n m…®keme, ‚ÄúJerusalem…®n itir D…®penir kam, an aven gumazamiziba nan ziamra f…® ikiam.‚Äù  
\v 5 Ez…® Manase, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven itir danganir uari akuvir pumuning…®n, an overiam…®n itir m…®kovezibar ziaba fasa, ofa gamir dakozir mabar ingari.  
\v 6 A Hinom…®n danganir zarim…®n iraghugha, uan otarir mabav soghez…® me ariaghirez…®, a ofan bar isia m…®gh…®rim…®n m…®n me tuez…® me bar isia m…®gh…®ri. Egha a uab…®n akuraghasa ariaghirezir gumazamizibar duabar diava, uaghan uab…®n akurvaghasa kukunir gumazibar azai, egha akavsiar igharagha garir av…®ribagh ami. Manase arazir kurar av…®riba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n dagh ami, ez…® an arazir kurar kaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God gamiz…®, a bar an…®ngaghe. 
\p  
\v 7 \x - \xo 33:7-8 \xt 1 Atriviba 9:3-5; 2 Eghaghaniba 7:12-18\x*Egha Manase aser amizim Aseran marvir guar kam inigha a isa Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven anet…®. Fom…®ra Ikiav…®ra Itir God, D…®penir kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha kamagh…®n Devit ko, an otarim Solomon m…®keme, ‚ÄúJerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam ko an itir D…®penir kam, k…® uab…® Israelian anababar tong…®n a ginaba, eght…® me zurara an iz…®, nan ziamra fam.  
\v 8 Ia nan gumazamiziba, k…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ia nan Arazir nan ingangarir gumazim, Moses, ia gan…®ngiziba ko, arazir k…® ifongeziba ko, bizir k…® damuasa ia m…®kemeziba, ia bar dar g…®n mang…®t…®, nguazir k…® fom…®ra ian inazir afeziabagh an…®ngiz…®, ia dat…®r…®gh…®n apiaghav itim, k…® an ia batueghan kogham.‚Äù  
\v 9 Ez…® Atrivim Manase Judaba ko, Jerusalemian n…®ghn…®zibagh amua me getuima me bar arazir kurabagh amuav…®ra iti. Ez…® men arazir kurar kaba, da gumazamizir fom…®ra nguazir kam…®n ikezibar arazir kurabagh afira. Gumazamizir kaba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God me batoghez…®, Israelia nguazir kam…®n aven ize. 
\s1 Manase navim g…®ra 
\p  
\v 10 Manase uan gumazamiziba ko, me amir arazir kuraba, Ikiav…®ra Itir God da atagh…®raghasa me m…®geima, me an akam baragha an g…®n zuir puvat…®.  
\v 11 Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Asirian atrivim…®n m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapaniba ko, an m…®dorozir gumaziba amangiz…®, me iza Judaba ko m…®sogha me ab…®ra. Egha Asiriaba kalabuziam…®n m…®n Manasen suiragha, akezim an atinim garugha, sen…®n an dafarimning ikegha, a inigha Babilon…®n ghu.  
\v 12 Ez…® a bar osemegha Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an ovavibar God…®n damazim…®n uab…® ab…®ragha, uamategha God bagha iza,  
\v 13 \x - \xo 33:13 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 5:20; Esra 8:23; Daniel 4:25\x*uab…®n akurvaghasa an azangs…®si. Ez…® God Manasen azangs…®zim baregha an akuragha anetaghiz…®, a uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghugha, ua kantri gativagha an gari. Egha Manase dat…®r…®gh…®n kamagh…®n fo, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a uab…®ra guizbang…®ra God. 
\p  
\v 14 Bizir kabar g…®n, Manase Jerusalem av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n azenan itir d…®vazir igiam…®n ingari. Me kamagh…®n danganir kam d…®bori, Devit…®n Nguibar Ekiam. D…®vazir kam…®n tuirivim bar p…®n iti. D…®vazim aruem uaghiri nagh…®n, danganir zarir Gihon…®n D…®par Em…®m…®rim…®n ikegha ghua not…®n amadaghan tiar akar me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n tu, Osiriba Amadir Tiar Akam. D…®vazim uaghan Ofel…®n m…®ghs…®am av…®ni. Egha Manase uaghan, Judan Distrigh…®n itir nguibar ekiar d…®vazir bar gavgaviba av…®nizibar ganasa, m…®dorozir gumazibar gumazir dapaniba am…®sefe.  
\v 15 Egha a ik…®zir igharazibar marvir guaba ko a uab…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven at…®zir aser nedazim batoke. Egha a uaghan, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim itir m…®ghs…®am…®n p…®n itir asebar ofa gamir dakoziba ko, Jerusalem…®n danganir igharazibar itir ofa gamir dakoziba sara akaraghar…®ki. Egha a bizir kaba inigha nguibar ekiam…®n azenan ghua bar ada makuni.  
\v 16 Egha a g…®n uamategha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir dakozim ak…®ri. Egha God ko navir vam…®ran ikiamin ofaba ko, God m…®namamin ofaba bagha, as…®ziba inigha iza ofa gamir dakozim…®n dar ofa gami. Egha a kamagh…®n Judabav gei, ‚ÄúIa Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelia en God, ia an ziam f…®.‚Äù  
\v 17 Ez…® gumazamiziba Atrivim Manasen akam baregha, ua asebar ziaba fer puvat…®. Me bar mogh…®ra Jerusalem…®n izir puvat…®. Me uan m…®ghs…®abar itir danganibara ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men God…®n ziam fa, egha ofaba a gan…®di. 
\s1 Atrivim Manase areme 
\r (2 Atriviba 21:17-18) 
\p  
\v 18 Atrivim Manase amizir arazir igharazibar eghaghaniba, ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n iti, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghanibar Ak…®nafarim. Manase God ko m…®kemezir m…®g…®r…®g…®aba ko, akam inigha izir gumaziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God…®n ziam…®n Manase m…®kemezir akar kaba, da uaghan ak…®nafarir kam…®n iti.  
\v 19 Ez…® Atrivim Manasen eghaghanir maba ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n iti, God…®n Akam Inigha Izir Gumazibar Eghaghaniba. Ak…®nafarir kam, Manasen arazir kurabagh eghara, an ak…®rim ragha God gasarazir arazim geghara, an asebar ziaba fer danganir a ingarizibagh eghara, egha a ingarizir guarir ak…®nir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itibagh eghara, egha marvir guar a ingarigha dar ziaba febar eghaghanibagh eghari. Ak…®nafarir kam uaghan, a navim giragha uab…® ab…®razir arazim ko, a God ko m…®geima, God an d…®mdiam baraghizir bizibagh eghari.  
\v 20 Manase uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremez…®, me atrivim…®n d…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven anefa. Ez…® an otarim Emon an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\s1 Emon Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 21:19-26) 
\p  
\v 21 Emon 22plan azeniba ikia egha atrivim…®n oto, egha azenir pumuningra Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike.  
\v 22 Emon…®n afeziam Manase amiz…® mogh…®n, Emon uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami. Amon…®n afeziam Manase fom…®ra ingarizir marvir guaba, a da bagha ofabagh amua dar ziaba fe.  
\v 23 Emon…®n afeziam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n uab…® ab…®ragha navim g…®ra, ez…® Emon kamagh…®n amizir puvat…®. An arazir kurabar os…®mt…®zim ghuav…®ra iti.  
\v 24 Dughiar mam…®n, Emon…®n ingangarir gumazibar dapaniba uari akuvagha, a m…®sueght…® an aremeghasa tuaviba buria akam m…®sosi. Egha me g…®n atrivim…®n d…®penim…®n aven a m…®soghez…® an areme.  
\v 25 Ez…® g…®n Judan gumazamiziba, ingangarir gumazibar dapanir Emon m…®soghezir kaba inigha, uaghan me m…®soghez…® me ariaghire. Egha me Emon…®n otarim Josaia gamiz…®, a uan afeziam…®n danganim inigha men atrivim…®n oto. 
\c 34  
\ms1 Atrivim Josaian eghaghanim 
\mr (Sapta 34--35) 
\s1 Josaia Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 22:1-2) 
\p  
\v 1 \x - \xo 34:1 \xt Jeremaia 3:6\x*Josaia 8plan azeniba ikia, Judan atrivim…®n oto, egha 31plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike.  
\v 2 Atrivim Josaia uan ovavim, Atrivim Devit fom…®ra amiz…® mogh…®n, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir aghuibagh ami. Egha a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akaba bar a dar g…®n mangasa bar gavgafi. 
\s1 Josaia asebar marvir guaba batuegha da makuni 
\p  
\v 3 \x - \xo 34:3 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 15:2\x*Josaia 15plan azeniba ikia, egha a namba 8…®n azenir an atrivim…®n itir dughiar kamra, a uan ovavim Atrivim Devit…®n God…®n ziam fa a baghav…®ra iti. An namba 12…®n azenir an atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, a uan ingangarir gumaziba amangiz…® me Juda ko Jerusalem…®n danganiba bar dagh arua, asebar ziaba fer danganir m…®ghs…®abar p…®n itiba bar dagh as…®ghas…®gha, temer guarir ak…®nir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itiba ko, marvir guar me temeba ko, ain…®n ingariziba, bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 34:4 \xt 2 Atriviba 21:3; 2 Eghaghaniba 33:3\x*A ghua garima, ingangarir gumaziba asem Bal…®n ofa gamir dakozibagh as…®ghas…®gha, dar borogh…®n itir paura mughuriar aghuim…®n ofabagh amir dakozibagh as…®ghas…®ki. Egha me temer guarir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itiba ko, temeba ko, ain…®n ingarizir aser mabar nedaziba sara as…®ghas…®gha, dav sozima da m…®saraghira averenim…®n m…®n oto. Egha me averenir kaba inigha ghua gumazamizir fom…®ra aser kabar ofa gamizibar mozibagh is…®n da kavamangi.  
\v 5 \x - \xo 34:5 \xt 1 Atriviba 13:2\x*Egha Josaia asebar ofa gamir gumazibar aghariba inigha, men ofa gamir dakozibagh is…®n da tuez…® da isi. A bizir kabagh amigha g…®vaz…®, Juda ko, Jerusalem Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n ua zue. 
\p  
\v 6 Egha Josaia ghua Manasen anabam…®n nguazim ko, Efraim…®n anabam ko, Simeon…®n anabam ko, Naptalin anabam…®n nguazim…®n ghua bar not…®n amadaghan tu. An arazir kamra, apaniba faragha as…®ghas…®ghizir nguibar ekiabar itir asebar ofa gamir dakoziba, a bar adagh as…®ghas…®ki.  
\v 7 A Israel…®n danganir kaba bar dagh arua, ofa gamir dakozibagh as…®ghas…®gha, temer guarir ak…®nir aser amizim Aseran nedazim itiba ko, aser igharazibar nedaziba sara, a bar adav sogha da m…®saraghar…®ghiz…® da averenim…®n m…®n oto. Egha a uaghan Israel…®n nguazim…®n aven, pauran mughuriar aghuim gamir dakoziba bar dagh as…®ghas…®ki. A ingangarir kam ag…®vagha, uamategha Jerusalem…®n ghu. 
\s1 Me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven, God…®n Arazibar Ak…®nafarim…®n api 
\r (2 Atriviba 22:3-20) 
\p  
\v 8 Atrivim Josaia 18plan azenibar atrivim…®n ikia, egha asebagh as…®ghas…®ghizir ingangarim ag…®vagha, a uan kantri ko, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim gamiz…®, aning God…®n damazim…®n zue. A g…®n gumazir 3pla amadaz…®, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an God…®n D…®penim uam anek…®r…®ghasamin ingangarim…®n ganasa ghue. Gumazir 3plan kabar ziabar kara: Asalian otarim Safan ko, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n garir gumazir dapanim Masea ko, atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim Joa, a Joahas…®n otarim.  
\v 9 Gumazir kaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itiar akam…®n garir Livaiba bagha ghue. Livaiba faragha God…®n D…®penim…®n ingangarim…®n akuraghasa, Manasen anabam…®n gumazamiziba ko, Efraim…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko, Israelian ikiav…®ra itir varazira ko, Judan anabam…®n adarazi ko, Benjamin…®n anabam…®n adarazi ko, Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n itir adarazi da, dag…®ar maba ini. Egha gumazir 3plan kaba, dag…®ar kaba inigha ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Hilkia bagha ghu.  
\v 10 Egha me dag…®ar kaba Hilkia gan…®ngiz…®, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®rir ingangarim…®n garir gumazibagh an…®ngiz…®, me D…®penim ak…®ramin ingangarir gumazibagh ivese.  
\v 11 Me, d…®penibar ingarir gumaziba ko, gumazir dag…®abar d…®penibar ingara fozibagh ivese. Ez…® me God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven d…®peniba uam adar ingarasa, d…®penir inogoriba ko, b…®rir aghariba ko, dag…®ar me d…®ghoregha ar…®ghiziba, dagh ivese. Fom…®ra Judan atriviba d…®penir kaba derav…®ram dar garir puvat…®z…®, da ikufi.  
\v 12 Gumazir d…®penir kabar ingariziba, me bar ingangarir aghuim gami. Atrivim…®n gumazir dapaniba, gumazir kabar ganasa Livain marazi am…®sefe. Livain kabar ziabar kara: Merarin ik…®zim…®n gumazir kamning Jahat ko, Obadia ko, Kohat…®n ik…®zim…®n gumazir kamning, Sekaraia ko, Mesulam. Ez…® Livain igharaziba, kar gitan guar av…®ribar m…®soghan bar foziba,  
\v 13 gumazir D…®penim…®n ingarasa biziba ateriba ko, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim av…®nizir d…®vazim…®n aven ingangarir guar av…®ribagh amibar gari. Ez…® Livain marazi ak…®nafariba osirima, marazi God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n garima, marazi ingangarir igharazibagh ami. 
\p  
\v 14 Livaiba dag…®ar gumazamiziba inigha Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n zuiba isav…®ra itima, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim, Hilkia, God…®n Araziba Itir Ak…®nafarir R…®ghizim…®n api. Kar Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelia bagha Moses gan…®ngizir Araziba.  
\v 15 Ez…® Hilkia kamagh…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim Safan m…®gei, ‚ÄúK…® ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir mam…®n api, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven iti. Ak…®nafarir kam, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Arazibar Akaba an iti.‚Äù Egha Hilkia ak…®nafarir kam isa Safan gan…®ngi. 
\p  
\v 16 Ez…® Safan g…®n ak…®nafarir kam inigha iza atrivim gan…®ga kamagh…®n a m…®gei, ‚ÄúE n…® m…®kemez…® mogh…®n biziba bar adagh ami.  
\v 17 E Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itir dag…®aba bar ada inigha d…®penim ak…®raghasir ingangaribar garir gumaziba ko, ingangarir gumazibagh an…®ngi.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 18 Egha Safan kamagh…®n m…®gei, ‚ÄúAtrivim, ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Hilkia, ak…®nafarir kam na gan…®ngi.‚Äù Egha an ak…®nafarir r…®ghizir kam onegha atrivim…®n damazim…®n a d…®bori. 
\p  
\v 19 Ez…® atrivim ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven itir God…®n Arazibar Akar kaba baregha, bar osemegha, uan korotiam ab…®ki.  
\v 20 Egha an ofa gamir gumazim Hilkia ko, Safan…®n otarim Ahikam, ko, Maikan otarim, Apdon ko, atrivim…®n ak…®nafariba osirir gumazim Safan ko, atrivim…®n ingangarir gumazim Asaia, a bar men diaz…® me izez…®, a kamagh…®n me m…®gei,  
\v 21 ‚ÄúGod…®n Arazibar Akaba itir Ak…®nafarir k…® dat…®r…®gh…®n inizir kam, a Ikiav…®ra Itir God ifongezir arazibar g…®n mangasa e m…®gei. Ez…® en inazir afeziaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar kaba batuegha g…®fa. Ez…® bizir kam bang…®n Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar en an…®ngaghe. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n e God…®n Ak…®nafarir kam…®n apigha g…®fa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, k…® kamaghsua, ia mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n azaragh fogh, k…® Jerusalemia ko, Judan gumazamiziba ko, Israel…®n ikiav…®ra itiba, e bizir manabar amuasa a ifonge.‚Äù  
\v 22 Gumazir kaba atrivim…®n akam baregha, me God…®n akam inigha izir amizir mam ko m…®k…®masa nguibar igiar Jerusalem…®n borogh…®n itim…®n ghu. Amizir kam…®n ziam, Hulda. Hulda a Salum…®n amuim, a gumazir ofa gamir gumaziba azuir korotiaba itir danganim…®n garim. Salum a Tokhat…®n otarim, egha Hasran igiavotarim. 
\p Hulda gumazir kabar akam baregha g…®vagha,  
\v 23 kamagh…®n men akam ikaragha ghaze, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, a kamagh…®n m…®gei: Ia gumazir ia amadazir kam Josaia bagh uamategh mang…®, kamagh…®n a m…®kemegh,  
\v 24 ‚ÄòK…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, k…® kamagh…®n m…®gei: Me Judan atrivim…®n damazim…®n d…®ponezir Ak…®nafarim…®n itir Akaba, k…® uab…® bar dar g…®n mang…®, Jerusalem ko, an itir gumazamiziba saram as…®ghasigham.  
\v 25 Gumazamizir ak…®rim ragha na gasarazir kaba, me asebar marvir guabar ofabagh ami. Ez…® men arazir kurar kam na gamiz…®ma, k…® puv…®ram atari. K…® Jerusalemia bar men an…®ngaghe, ez…® nan an…®ngagharir kam, a g…®vaghan kogham. 
\p  
\v 26 ‚Äú‚Äâ‚ÄòEz…® dat…®r…®gh…®n k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God, k…® kamagh…®n Judan atrivim m…®k…®masa. Me n…® bagha Ak…®nafarir kam d…®borima,  
\v 27 n…® bizir k…® Jerusalem ko, an itir gumazamizibar amuasa m…®kemeziba, n…® dagh fo. K…® kamagh…®n m…®gei, Jerusalem bar ikuvigh pura danganir k…®nim ikiam. Ez…® atrivim, n…® akar kam baregha navim giragha, nan damazim…®n uab…® ab…®ra. Egha n…® dat…®r…®gh…®n uan korotiam abigha, aziava nan dei. Kamagh…®n k…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God, kamagh…®n n…® m…®gei, k…® n…®n d…®mdiam baraki.  
\v 28 Egh k…® n…® ateght…®, n…® uab…® Jerusalem…®n otivamin as…®ghas…®zir kam…®n ganighan kogham. Puvat…®. N…® bar deraghv…®ra ikiam. Egh n…® g…®n uan inazir afeziabar m…®n aremeght…®, me n…®n kuam afagh g…®vaght…®, k…® Jerusalem ko, an itir darazigh as…®ghas…®gham.‚Äô‚Äâ‚Äù God…®n akam inigha izir amizim Hulda, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam gumazir kabagh anigha g…®vaz…®, me akar kam inigha atrivim bagha uamategha ghue. 
\s1 Gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n apengan ikiasa akam ak…®ri 
\r (2 Atriviba 23:1-20) 
\p  
\v 29 Ez…® Atrivim Josaia Juda ko, Jerusalem…®n gumazir dapanibar diaz…®, me iza uari akufa.  
\v 30 Ez…® atrivim ko, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba ko, Judan gumazamiziba ko, Jerusalem…®n itir gumazamiziba, me ghua Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n uari akufa. Me uari akuvagha g…®vaz…®, atrivim Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim itir Ak…®nafarir R…®ghizir me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n apizir kam inigha, an itir akaba bar me bagha da d…®bori.  
\v 31 Atrivim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akam…®n borogh…®n itir guarir ak…®nim…®n borogh…®n tughav ikia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim gamua kamagh…®n m…®gei: A bar guizbang…®ra uan navir averiam ko, uan duam…®n aven, God…®n Akar Gavgaviba ko, arazir a me gan…®ngiziba ko, arazir a ifongeziba, a bar dar amuam. Egh an Ak…®nafarir kam…®n aven itir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n akaba bar dar g…®n mangam.  
\v 32 Egha Benjamin…®n adarazi ko, Jerusalem…®n itir igharazi darasi, me Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavir kam…®n akabar g…®nt…®ghasa, atrivim m…®g…®r…®g…®ar bar gavgavim me gan…®ngi. Egha g…®n Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba, me uan ovavibar God ko amizir Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n akabar g…®nt…®si.  
\v 33 Israelian danganiba bar asebar marvir guaba dar ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® bizir kaba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n bizir bar kurar a bar aghuaziba. Ez…® Josaia marvir guar kaba bar adagh as…®ghas…®ki, egha Israelia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, uan God…®n g…®nt…®ghasa, bar gavgafi. Ez…® an atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, gumazamiziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God, men ovavibar God…®n g…®nt…®ghasa bar gavgafi, egha me anetaghizir puvat…®. 
\c 35  
\s1 Me God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam gami 
\r (2 Atriviba 23:21-23) 
\p  
\v 1 Atrivim Josaia m…®kemez…®, me God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam gami. Me iza Jerusalem…®n uari akuvagha, iak…®nir faragha zuim…®n, an aruer namba 14…®n, me dughiar ekiar kam g…®n…®ghn…®gha ofa damuasa sipsip…®n nguzir bar av…®ribav soke.  
\v 2 Ez…® Josaia ofa gamir gumazibav g…®a ghaze, ia uamategh Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n uan ingangarim damu. Egha me derav…®ra ingangarir kam damuasa, a uaghan gavgavim men n…®ghn…®zibagh an…®di. 
\p  
\v 3 Egha a uaghan akar mam Livaibagh an…®ngi, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n adarazira, me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n Israelian sure damuamin ingangarim iti. An m…®g…®r…®g…®am kamak…®n, ‚ÄúIa mang…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam inigh, uan d…®p…®zibar aneter mang…®, Devit…®n otarim Solomon fom…®ra ingarizir D…®penim…®n aven anet…®gh. Egh ia ua Akar D…®k…®r…®zir Gavgavim…®n Boksiam ater mang…® izegh damuan kogham, mati ia fom…®ra ami mok…®n. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, ian God…®n D…®penim…®n ingangariba, ia derav…®ra dar amu. Egh ia uaghan derav…®ra Israelian akurvagh, kar God…®n gumazamiziba.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 35:4 \xt 2 Eghaghaniba 8:14\x*Atrivim Devit ko, an otarim Atrivim Solomon ak…®nafarim osiriz…® mogh…®n, ia ik…®ziba vaghvagh dar gumaziba vaghvagh mang…® ik…®zir igharazibar gumaziba ko, ia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven ingangarir vabaram amiba bagh uari ak…®r.  
\v 5 Ian ik…®ziba vaghvagh Israelian anababar ik…®zibar akurvaghs…®, uan danganibar tuivigh me m…®zuam ik…®.  
\v 6 Ia God…®n damazim…®n uari zuamin arazim…®n g…®n mang…® uari zuegh, God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam bagh, ofa damus…® sipsip…®n nguzibav sogh. Egh ia ofan kam damus…® biziba ak…®r, eght…® Israelia ofan kam…®n araziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Moses m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, deraghv…®ra dar g…®n mangam.‚Äù 
\p  
\v 7 Gumazamiziba ofa damuasa Atrivim Josaia uab…® sipsip…®n nguzir bar av…®rim ko, memen nguziba ko, bulmakaun apuriba inigha gumazamizibagh an…®ngi. Sipsip…®n nguziba ko, memen nguzibar d…®bobonim, 30,000, ez…® bulmakaun apuribar d…®bobonim 3,000.  
\v 8 Ez…® atrivim…®n gumazir dapaniba, ofa damuasa uaghan as…®zir av…®riba gumazamiziba ko, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaibagh an…®ngi. Ez…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapanim Hilkia ko, God…®n D…®penim…®n garir gumazir igharazimning Sekaraia ko Jehiel, me dughiar ekiar kam…®n uaghan ofa damuasa, sipsip…®n nguzir bar av…®riba ko, memen nguziba inigha ofa gamir gumazibagh an…®ngi. Dar d…®bobonim, 2,600…®n tu. Egha me 300plan bulmakaun apuriba inigha, God bagh ofa damuasa, ofa gamir gumazibagh an…®ngi.  
\v 9 Ez…® Livaibar gumazir dapanir faragha zuir kaba, Konania uan dozimning Semaia ko, Netanel ko, Livain igharazir kaba: Hasabia ko, Jeiel Josabat, me sipsip…®n nguzir av…®riba ko, memen nguzir bar av…®riba ini, dar d…®bobonim 5,000…®n tu. Egha 500 bulmakaun apuriba sara ini, ez…® as…®zir kaba bar, me da isa Livaibagh an…®ngi. Eght…® me God, Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam bagh, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damuam. 
\p  
\v 10 Me ofa damuasa biziba bar da ak…®righa g…®vagha, atrivim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba ghua ofa gamir dakozim…®n borogh…®n, uan danganibar tuifi.  
\v 11 Ez…® Livaiba sipsipba ko, memebav suegha, dar ghuziba inigha ofa gamir gumazibagh an…®ngi. Ez…® ofa gamir gumaziba ghuziba inigha, ofa gamir dakozim…®n da kavamadi. Ez…® Livaiba as…®zir iniba amsi.  
\v 12 Moses Osirizir Arazibar Ak…®nafarim m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Livaiba as…®ziba aghoregha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa damuasa ofan bar isia m…®gh…®ribar ofa gamir dakozim…®n tuamin as…®zir tuziba isa, vaghvagha ik…®zibar gumazamizibagh an…®ngi. Livaiba arazir kamra m…®soghezir bulmakaubagh ami.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 35:13 \xt Ua Me Ini 12:8-9\x*Ofan kam…®n bizir God damuasa me m…®kemez…® mogh…®n, Livaiba sipsipba ko, memebar tuziba inigha avim…®n da tue. Egha me bulmakaun tuziba inigha, m…®ner ruariba ko, m…®ner epert…®zibar da avisi. Ez…® as…®zir tuzir kaba bar isigha g…®vaz…®, me zuam…®ra da inigha ghua gumazamizibagh an…®di.  
\v 14 Egha g…®n Livaiba uari uari bagha as…®zir tuziba tua egha ofa gamir gumaziba bagha uaghan maba tue, me Aron…®n ovavir boriba. Ofa gamir gumaziba ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riba bagha bar ingangarir ekiam gamua, dar ovibar ofa gamua zuima am…®nim p…®ri. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, me uari uari bagha as…®zir tuzitaba tuezir puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 15 \x - \xo 35:15 \xt 1 Eghaghaniba 25:1\x*Ez…® ighiaba banger gumaziba kar Asap…®n ovavir boriba, me God…®n D…®penim…®n uan danganibar tuivighav iti, mati Atrivim Devit ko, Asap ko, Heman ko, atrivim…®n akam inigha izir gumazim Jedutun, fom…®ra me m…®kemez…® mogh…®n ami. Ez…® Livain maba God…®n D…®penim…®n tiar akabar garir ingangarim gamua vaghvagha tiar akabar gara iti. Ez…® Livain igharaziba me bagha as…®zir tuziba tue. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, tiar akabar garir gumazir kaba ingangarir danganiba atagh…®raghs…® n…®ghn…®ghan kogham. 
\p  
\v 16 Aruer kam…®n, me God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam gami. Egha me ofan bar isia m…®gh…®riziba Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n ofa gamir dakozim…®n dagh ami, mati Atrivim Josaia damuasa me m…®kemez…® mok…®n.  
\v 17 \x - \xo 35:17 \xt Ua Me Ini 12:1-20\x*Israel…®n gumazamizir Jerusalem…®n itiba, me dughiar kam…®n isar kam gami. Egha me 7plan aruebar kagh ikia ghuav…®ra itima, Yis Puvat…®zir Bret…®n Isam Damuamin Dughiam ghua g…®fa.  
\v 18 Me God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isam gamiz…®, a bar deraghav…®ram oto. A God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isar Israelia fom…®ra amizibagh afira, kar akam inigha izir gumazim Samuel…®n dughiam…®n ikegha, iza Atrivim Josaian dughiam…®n tu. Atrivir igharaziba isar kam gamiz…®, a deragha otozir puvat…®. Ez…® dat…®r…®gh…®n Atrivim Josaia, ofa gamir gumaziba ko, Livaiba ko, Judaba ko, Israelia ko, Jerusalemia, me bar isar kam gamiz…®, a bar deraghav…®ram oto.  
\v 19 Dughiar kam…®n, Josaia 18plan azenibar atrivim…®n itima, me God Israelia Gitazir Dughiam G…®n…®ghn…®ghamin Isar kam bar deraghv…®ram a gami. 
\s1 Isipia Judaba ko m…®sogha Josaia m…®soghez…®, an areme 
\r (2 Atriviba 23:28-30) 
\p  
\v 20 Atrivim Josaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim ak…®rizir bizir kabar g…®n, Isip…®n Atrivim Neko, apaniba ko, m…®soghasa Isip…®n m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha Yufretis…®n Fanem…®n borogh…®n itir Karkemis…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu. Josaia bizir kam…®n akam baregha uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha Isipia ko, m…®soghasa zui.  
\v 21 Ez…® Atrivim Neko kamagh…®n Josaia bagha akam amaga ghaze, ‚ÄúO Judan atrivim, k…® adariba n…®n puvat…®, egha n…® ko m…®soghasa izir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® tizim bagha na m…®soghasa? God na ko ikia, egha apanibav soghasa nan av…®ra, ez…® k…® mang…® merara m…®soghasa. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, n…® God…®n anogoroghan mark…®. Puvat…®ght…®ma, a n…® gas…®ghasigham.‚Äù  
\v 22 God m…®g…®r…®g…®ar kam Atrivim Nekon akam…®n Josaia gan…®ngiz…® an a baregha, m…®dorozim bagha bar ifuegha bar otoke. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Isipia deragh an gan a g…®fofoghan koghasa, an atrivir korotiam suegha, korotiar igharazim aru. Egha a uan m…®dorozir gumaziba inigha m…®soghasa Megidon danganir zarim giraghugha, Isipia ko m…®sosi.  
\v 23 Me m…®sogha, Isipian m…®dorozir gumaziba uan barir pibar Judabar amadaghan asavamaga, egha Josaia gase. 
\p Ez…® a kamagh…®n uan ingangarir gumazibav gei, ‚ÄúK…® kuram inigha g…®fa. Ia na inigh m…®dorozir danganim ategh mang…® igharagh na at…®gh.‚Äù  
\v 24 Ez…® me karis…®n a itim…®n a inigha karis…®n igharazim gat…®gha, a inigha Jerusalem…®n ghu. Ez…® an aremez…®ma, me an kuam isa an inazir afeziabar mozibar borogh…®n anefa. Ez…® Judaba ko, Jerusalem…®n gumazamiziba, me bar Atrivim Josaian kuarkuvigha, a bagha puv azi.  
\v 25 Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia, Atrivim Josaia bagha azirakar ighiar mam osiri. Ez…® dughiar kam…®n iza dat…®r…®gh…®n, gumaziba ko amizir azir akabagh amiba, me Atrivim Josaia g…®n…®ghn…®gha azirakar ighiar kam gamuav…®ra iti. Ez…® os…®mt…®zibar dughiabar, Israelia zurara arazir kam…®n g…®n ghua azirakar kam gami. Azirakar ighiar kam, Azir Akabar Ak…®nafarim…®n iti.  
\v 26-27 Atrivim Josaia amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba, da dughiar an atrivir ingangarim faraghav…®ra itim…®n ikegha ghua, an aremezir dughiam…®n tu, da ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n iti, Judaba ko, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghanibar Ak…®nafarim. Ak…®nafarir kam uaghan, Josaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n Ak…®nafarim…®n Osirizir Arazibar g…®nt…®gha amizir arazir aghuibagh eghari. 
\c 36  
\ms1 Apaniba kantri Juda gas…®ghas…®ki 
\mr (Sapta 36) 
\s1 Joahas Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 23:30-35) 
\p  
\v 1 Josaian ovevem…®n g…®n, Judaba, an otarim Joahas inigha, borem an dapanim gingegha, anem…®sevez…® a uan afeziam…®n danganim inigha men atrivim…®n oto.  
\v 2 Joahas 23plan azeniba ikia Judabar atrivim…®n oto. Egha iak…®nir 3plara Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike.  
\v 3 Isip…®n Atrivim Neko Jerusalem…®n iza, atrivir ingangarim…®n Joahas ag…®fa. Ez…® Joahas uam atrivim…®n itir puvat…®. Ez…® Atrivim Neko Judan kantrin gumazamizibagh amima, me takis…®n m…®n dag…®aba a gan…®di, dar d…®bobonim, 3,400 kilogrem silva ko 34 kilogrem gol.  
\v 4 \x - \xo 36:4 \xt Jeremaia 22:11-12\x*Ez…® Atrivim Neko, Joahas…®n dozim Eliakim inigha a gamiz…®, a Joahas…®n danganim inigha Juda ko, Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n oto. Neko Eliakim…®n ziam adegha ziam Jehoiakim a gat…®. Egha g…®n, Neko Joahas inigha Isip…®n ghugha kalabuziar gumazim…®n m…®n anet…®. 
\s1 Jehoiakin Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 23:36--24:7) 
\p  
\v 5 \x - \xo 36:5 \xt Jeremaia 22:18-19; 26:1-6; 35:1-19\x*Jehoiakim 25plan azeniba ikia, Judabar atrivim…®n oto. Egha 11plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike. Jehoiakim Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami.  
\v 6 \x - \xo 36:6 \xt Jeremaia 25:1-38; 36:1-32; 45:1-5; Daniel 1:1-2\x*Jehoiakim Judabar atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, Babilonian Atrivim Nebukatnesar uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iza Judan kantri m…®sosi. Egha Nebukatnesar me ab…®ragha Atrivim Jehoiakim…®n suiragha kalabuziar gumazim…®n m…®n senbar a ikegha, a inigha Babilon…®n nguibar ekiam…®n ghu.  
\v 7 Egha Nebukatnesar uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven itarir ekiar maba ko, itarir dozir maba inigha Babilon…®n ghugha, uan atrivir d…®penim…®n da ar…®ki. 
\p  
\v 8 Atrivim Jehoiakim amizir bizir igharazibar eghaghaniba, ak…®nafarir me kamagh…®n d…®borim…®n iti, Judaba ko, Israelian Atrivibar Eghaghanibar Ak…®nafarim. Ak…®nafarir kam uaghan Jehoiakim…®n arazir kuraba ko, an amizir bizir bar kurar God bar aghuazibagh eghari. Ez…® an otarim Jehoiakin, an danganim inigha atrivim…®n oto. 
\s1 Jehoiakin Judan atrivim…®n iti 
\r (2 Atriviba 24:8-17) 
\p  
\v 9 Jehoiakin 8plan azeniba ikia, Judan atrivim…®n oto. Egha 3plan iak…®niba ko, 10plan aruebara Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike. Egha a Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n damazim…®n arazir kurabagh ami.  
\v 10 \x - \xo 36:10 \xt Jeremaia 22:24-30; 24:1-10; 29:1-2; 37:1; Esekiel 17:12-13\x*Azenir kam…®n, orangt…®zim…®n dughiam g…®vasava amima, Atrivim Nebukatnesar m…®dorozir gumaziba amadaz…®, me ghua Jehoiakin isa kalabuziar gumazim…®n m…®n, a inigha Babilon…®n ghu. Egha m…®dorozir gumaziba uaghan Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n aven itir itarir aghuiba inigha Babilon…®n ghu. Egha Nebukatnesar Jehoiakin…®n afeziar dozim Sedekaia gamiz…®, a Juda ko Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n oto.\f + \fr 36:10 \ft 2 Eghaghaniba 36:9 kamagh…®n m…®gei, Jehoiakin 8pla azenibara ikia egha atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® 2 Atriviba 24:8 kamagh…®n m…®gei, Jehoiakin 18pla azenibara ikia atrivim…®n oto. Ez…® 2 Eghaghaniba 36:10 ghaze, Sedekaia a Jehoiakin…®n Avebam. Ez…® 2 Atriviba 24:17 ghaze, Sedekaia a Jehoiakin…®n afeziar dozim. Fofozir gumazir av…®ribar n…®ghn…®zim, akar 2 Atrivibar itim, a guizbang…®ra, ez…® akar 2 Eghaghanibar itim, a guizbang…®ra puvat…®.\f* 
\s1 Babilonia Jerusalemia ko m…®sogha nguibar ekiam ini 
\r (2 Atriviba 24:18--25:21; Jeremaia 52:1-11) 
\p  
\v 11 \x - \xo 36:11 \xt Jeremaia 27:1-22; 28:1-17\x*Sedekaia 21plan azeniba ikia, Judan atrivim…®n oto. Egha 11plan azenibar Jerusalem…®n atrivim…®n ike.  
\v 12 Sedekaia Ikiav…®ra Itir God, an God…®n damazim…®n, arazir kurabagh ami. Ez…® akam inigha izir gumazim, Jeremaia, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n akam…®n gun a m…®geima, a uab…® ab…®rava an akam barazir puvat…®.  
\v 13 \x - \xo 36:13 \xt Esekiel 17:15\x*Sedekaia bar akaba barazi puvat…®gha, navim giraghan aghuagha, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, Israelian God bagh, uamategh izan aghua. Nebukatnesar faragha uab…®n g…®n mangasa Akar Gavgavim…®n Sedekaia gamiz…®, a pura God…®n ziam d…®bora ghaze, a zurara Nebukatnesar…®n akam…®n g…®nt…®gham. Egha Sedekaia uaghan Atrivim Nebukatnesar…®n akaba barazir puvat…®gha, uam an apengan itir puvat…®.  
\v 14 Ez…® ofa gamir gumazibar dapaniba ko, gumazamiziba bar mogh…®ra ak…®rim ragha Ikiav…®ra Itir God gasaragha, kantrin igharazibar arazir bar kurar God bar aghuazibagh amua ghuav…®ra iti. Me kamagh…®n amua, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penir Jerusalem…®n itir a ua baghav…®ra inabazim gamima, an an damazim…®n m…®ze.  
\v 15 Ez…® men inazir afeziabar God, a uan D…®penim ko, uan gumazamizibar apangkuvigha, iv…®ghv…®gha me m…®k…®masa uan akam inigha izir gumaziba amangi.  
\v 16 Ez…® gumazamiziba, akam inigha izir gumazibar akabar aghuagha dar abara me d…®povav…®ra iti, ez…® Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n an…®ngagharim oto. Egha an an…®ngagharir kam an gumazamizibar ikiav…®ra iti, ez…® me a gitav…®raghan tuaviba puvat…®. 
\p  
\v 17 \x - \xo 36:17 \xt Jeremaia 21:1-10; 34:1-5\x*Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God Babilon…®n atrivim amadaz…®, a uan m…®dorozir gumaziba ko iza m…®dorozir sababar Judabagh as…®ghas…®ki. Egha me Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n ghua gumazir igiabav soghez…® me ariaghire. Atrivim gumazir igiaba ko, amizir igiaba ko, gumazamizir ghuriba ko, amughamughiziba sara, bar tong men apangkuvizir puvat…®. Ikiav…®ra Itir God bar Judaba isa Babilon…®n atrivim…®n dafarim gat…®.  
\v 18 Ez…® Babilon…®n atrivim, Ikiav…®ra Itir God…®n D…®penim…®n itir itarir ekiaba ko, itarir doziba ko, bizir bar aghuiba, ko, Judan atrivim ko, an gumazir dapanibar bizir bar aghuiba, a bar da inigha Babilon…®n ghu.  
\v 19 \x - \xo 36:19 \xt 1 Atriviba 9:8\x*Ez…® Babilonia God…®n D…®penim gaborogha Jerusalem av…®nizir d…®vaziba bar ada akaraghar…®ki. Egha nguibam…®n aven atrivir d…®penim ko, d…®penir aghuir igharaziba bar dagh apongez…® da isi. Egha bizir iveziba bar p…®n kozibagh as…®ghas…®ki.  
\v 20 Babilon…®n atrivim gumazamizir m…®dorozim…®n ariaghirezir puvat…®ziba inigha ghua Babilon…®n kalabuziar gumazamizibar m…®n me ar…®ki. Ez…® me pura men ingangarir gumazamizir k…®nibar m…®n ikia ghua, kantri Persia tugha gavgavigha, Babilon d…®kab…®razir dughiam oto.  
\v 21 \x - \xo 36:21 \xt Jeremaia 25:11; 29:10\x*Israelia fom…®ra uan nguazim…®n ikia, egha 7plan azenibar vaghvagha dar aven azenir vam…®ra avughsazim nguazim gan…®ngizir puvat…®. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, Ikiav…®ra Itir God faragha Jeremaian akam garugha m…®kemezir akam, guizbang…®ram otivasa, Israelia ghua 70plan azenibar Babilon…®n kalabuziabar m…®n iti. Ez…® men nguazim puram avughsa iti.\f + \fr 36:21 \ft N…® Ofa Gami 26:33-35, ko Jeremaia 25:11 ko 29:10…®n gan.\f* 
\s1 Atrivim Sairus kamagh…®n m…®gei, Judaba uamategh uan nguibam…®n mang…® 
\r (Esra 1:1-3) 
\p  
\v 22 Sairus kantri Persian atrivim…®n itir dughiam…®n, an azenir faraghav…®ra zuim…®n, Ikiav…®ra Itir God, akam inigha izir gumazim Jeremaia m…®kemezir akam damight…®, a guiz…®n otivasa, a Sairus…®n n…®ghn…®zim fez…®, an akar kam osirigha, a isa nguazir an ativagha gariba bagha bar da amangi. Eght…® akar kam nguazir an ativaziba bar dar mang…®t…®, gumazir akar kam inigha zuiba, gumazamiziba bagh a d…®ponam.  
\v 23 \x - \xo 36:23 \xt Aisaia 44:28\x*Kar Persian atrivim Sairus…®n m…®g…®r…®g…®am, ‚ÄúIkiav…®ra Itir God, a God…®n uan Nguibam…®n itim, a nguazim…®n itir kantriba bar na gan…®ngiz…®, k…® dagh atifa. Egha Judan Distrigh…®n aven Jerusalem…®n nguibar ekiam…®n, uan D…®penim…®n ingarasa na am…®sefe. Ikiav…®ra Itir God, a Israelia ian God, ia an gumazamiziba, ez…® a ia ko iti. Kamagh…®n amiz…®, ia uamategh Jerusalem…®n nguibam…®n mavanangam.‚Äù